Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你可曾听过\NHave you not heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,耶和华是永恒之神\NThe Lord is the everlasting God,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,创造地极之主\Nthe Creator of the ends of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,他既不疲乏 也不困倦\NHe will not grow tired or weary,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,他的智慧无人可揣度\Nand His understanding no one can fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他赐力量予疲乏者\NHe gives strength to the weary
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,增能力予软弱者\Nand increases the power of the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,正值青春亦会疲惫困倦\NEven youths grow tired and weary,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,青年亦会绊倒跌跤\Nand young men stumble and fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但那些仰望上帝者\NBut those who hope in the Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,必重新得力\Nwill renew their strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必展翅翱翔如鹰\NThey will soar on wings like eagles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必奔跑 而不疲倦\NThey will run and not grow weary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,他们必行走 而不跌倒\NThey will walk and not be faint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德 坚持住\NDesmond, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 德斯蒙德\NHang on, Desmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会带你离开这儿\NWe're going to get you out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德\NDesmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.91,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德\NDesmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.44,0:03:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等嘛 - 跟上嘛\N- Wait up. - Catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,等等嘛 我有事要告诉你\NWait up, I've got something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？哈尔\NWhat, Hal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,到顶者赢\NRace you to the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 骗子\NHey! Cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 回头见 笨伯 - 嘿\N- See you later, slowpoke. - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.81,0:03:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,搭把手\NWant a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.97,0:03:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我能行\NI got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.44,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,下去吧\NSit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- 别闹 - 走你\N- don't quit it. - You quit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝保佑\NFor Pete's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 离悬崖远点 该死的傻孩子\NHey! Get away from that ledge, you damn fool kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.66,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,想摔断脖子吗\NYou're going to break your necks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是多斯的儿子 跟老爹一样疯狂\NIt's them Doss kids. Crazy as their old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们挖掘了杰克埋骨之地\NThey dug up the corner of Jackson and Main...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把他放在人行道上\NPutting in a sidewalk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你们现已认不出来啦\NYou boys wouldn't recognize it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉你 我怀疑他们会认出你\NMind you, I doubt they'd recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.65,0:04:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他们几乎认不出我 当我路过\NThey hardly know me when I walk by 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好象我跟你一起死了\NIt's like I died with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好象我们从未存在过\NIt's like we boys never existed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 今天就说这些\NWell, that's all I got for you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.38,0:05:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,用右手挡住他 德斯蒙德\NBlock him with your right, Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.49,0:05:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,别打了 听到了吗\NStop it! Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们干嘛打架 - 他们何需有理\N- What are they fighting about? - When'd they ever need a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.68,0:05:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆 你能\NTom! do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.47,0:05:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,何必阻止而让我两个都打\NWhy stop 'em? Saves me whipping them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我只需打那个赢的\NThis way, I just whip the one that wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆\NTorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 天啦\NOh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆 醒醒 你能听到吗\NTom! Wake up, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你怎么能这样 - 他听不到我\N- What the hell have you done? - He can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得拿些冰块\NI'll get some ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- 把那个篮子拿开 - 好的\N- You shift that basket. - I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他在呼吸吗\NIs he breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔 哈尔你能听到吗\NHal? Hal, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔你能听到吗\NHal, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔\NHal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 拜托\NCome on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他瞳孔在扩张\NHe's dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔\NHal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你做事不经大脑吗\NWhat do you think you're doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.88,0:07:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在必须打你 你知道规则\NI'm gonna have to beat you now, you know the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,听到没 德斯蒙德\NYou hear me, Desmond?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,- 德斯蒙德 - 汤姆 住手\N- Desmond! - Tom, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这样教育不了他\NWhat's that gonna teach the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他的暴行已经够多了\NHe's violent enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了 赏他一个令人窒息的吻\NOkay, fine, you go smother him in kisses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他这世界是个既柔软又温暖之处\NYou tell him the world's a soft and gentle place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哈尔会好的\NHal's gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.26,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我差点杀了他\NI could have killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:07:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 你差点\NYes, you could have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谋杀是众恶之首\NMurder, it's the worst sin of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,取人性命\NAnd to take another man's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,则是最严重之罪在主眼里\Nthat is the most egregious sin in the Lord's sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再没别的能令他更伤心\NNothing hurts his heart so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.03,0:08:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你听不懂人话吗？\NDon't you understand English?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.99,0:08:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再说一次吗？\NDo I have to tell you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你滚开 婆娘 否者我要动手了\NYou move, woman, or I will wallop you good and hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在闹什么呢 你没事吧 伯莎\NWhat the hell's going on? You okay, Bertha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你在意你自己的破事\NYou mind your own damned business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,去睡觉吧 汤姆\NGo sleep it off, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨他\NI hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.14,0:08:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈\NMomma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么如此恨我们\NWhy does he hate us so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 他不恨我们\NOh, he don't hate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他恨自己\NHe hates himself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有时\Nsometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你爸爸 我见过真实的他\NYour daddy tonight, that ain't the real him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你了解他 就像战前我那样\NI wish you knew him like I did, before the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们唱得如何？德斯蒙德\NHow'd we sound, Desmond?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就像天使 妈\NLike a heavenly host of angels, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你知 撒谎可是罪 尤其在此地\NNow, you know it's a sin to tell a lie, especially in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我可从未说过她们是唱歌的天使\NWell, I ain't never said they were singing angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,外面怎么了？德斯蒙德\NWhat's going on out there? Desmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,继续 拉出来 拉出来\NGet it up, get it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.60,0:10:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拖出来 拖吧\NDrag him out. Just the tarp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我打电话叫救护车\NI'll phone an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没时间了 找辆皮卡\NNo, no time. Joshua's pickup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 要快 - 好的\N- Quick! - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你会好的 伙计 你会好的\NYou're going to be fine now. You're going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你是专家 - 我看看\N- You're in good hands. - I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,何处受伤\NWhat have we got here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,动脉切断 拿些缝线来\NIt's a severed artery. Get some sutures.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 医生\NYes, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,稍稍用力按住它 是你用此止血的\NPut some pressure on it. Did you apply this tourniquet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 先生 - 干得不错\N- Yes, sir. - Nice work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.53,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你可救了这孩子一命\NYou might have saved this boy's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.35,0:10:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你住我们这儿 - 你会好的\N- You staying with us? - You're going to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字 孩子\NWhat's your name, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.77,0:10:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔伯特\NGilbert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 动手术？- 对 动手术\N- Surgery? - Yeah, surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:10:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,住我们这儿 你会好的\NStay with us, you're gonna be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.16,0:11:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉痛吗？\NYou feel pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.25,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,住这里 好吗？\NStay with us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.21,0:12:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,部队体检在那边 这里是献血\NArmy physicals that way. This is for giving blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.98,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,哦不 那不是我的 我很好\NOh, no, that's not mine. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你的问询 女士\NThank you for asking though, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.52,0:12:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你要什么\NWhat do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我的皮带\NMy belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它借给出车祸的男生\NI lent it to the boy who had the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没它我的裤子系不好\NMy pants don't hold up so good without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我可没有你的皮带\NWell, uh, I don't have your belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我知女士\NNo, I know that, ma'am. It's out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,它仍在男生那儿\NIt's right out there with the boy still.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.78,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我在此采血\NI'm just here to take blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你我的\NI'll give mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 去那个房间 跟别人一起等\NOkay, go to that room over there and wait with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会叫你\NI'll call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 那个房间\NThat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.88,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前献过血吗 先生\NYou ever given blood before, Mr...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,多斯\NDoss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但朋友们都叫我德斯蒙德 不 女士这是我第一次\NBut my friends call me Desmond. No, ma'am, this is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我总梦想成为医生 只是呢\NI always dreamed about being a doctor. But, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没念多少书\NI didn't get much school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可能有点头晕 采完后\NYou may be a little dizzy when we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有人接你吗\NIs somebody picking you up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,没 女士 我走回去\NNo, ma'am. Walking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你住哪儿\NWhere do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,福特哈姆 女士\NFort Hill, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那挺远的\NThat's a ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,五或六英里\NNo. Just five or six miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿过树林\Nbut I cut through the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那就七英里\NIt's seven that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.38,0:14:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,必是因喜欢树林\NYou must really like the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的女士 确实是\NYes, ma'am. I sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 轻压此处\NOkay, put some pressure here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.31,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.94,0:14:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,再见\NBye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.60,0:14:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是要去哪儿？看起来整洁帅气\NWhere you going looking all spruced and nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,去见昨天的人\NMet someone yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.86,0:14:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,医院护士\NA nurse over at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,名叫多萝西舒特 我要娶她\NHer name's Dorothy Schutte. I'm gonna marry her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,天啦 她知道吗\NGoodness. Does she know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还没呢 不过快了\NWell, not yet. She's about to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟女人说过话吗？\NYou ever even spoken to a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,除了这个你妈妈之外\NI mean, one that's not family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,跟她说过\NSpoke to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 既如此 给你兄弟来个大大的拥抱 - 哈尔\N- Well, in that case, come give your brother a big hug. - Hal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,过来\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让你的油爪离我远点儿\NKeep your greasy paws off of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,祝我好运 妈妈\NWish me luck, Momma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\NGood luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个\NNext.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,随便坐\NGrab a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你以前献过血吗\NYou ever given blood before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 女士 我有\NYes, ma'am. I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你 皮带男\NYou're the belt man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德 是的 女士\NDesmond, yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 德斯蒙德 我们不能连续两天采你的血\NWell, Desmond, we can't take your blood two days in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那就好 可否拿回我的\NWell, that's good. I came to get mine back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的啥 - 我的血 我想要回来\N- You what? - My blood. I need it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那不行 不能把它还你\NWell, it don't work like that, we can't just give it back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你必需还\NWell, you got to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,自从你用针扎了我 我就心跳加速\NEver since you stuck me with that needle, my heart's been beating real fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,每次想到你则会跳得更快\NEvery time I think about you, it beats faster still.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前从未听过这话 好土\NI never heard that one before. It's pretty corny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？\NIt is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个耻辱 我练了一整夜\NThat's a shame, I done practiced that all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不好吗\NNo good?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.46,0:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我没那样说\NI didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.23,0:16:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有何差异？动脉跟静脉\NWhat's the difference between an artery and a vein?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你说啥 - 男孩的车祸\N- What are you talking about? - The boy's accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,动脉喷血\NArteries spurt blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,静脉呢\NAnd veins?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.19,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,流血\NBleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得你得多练习\NI think you need to practice
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,男生跟 女生的约会对白 在你出门前\Nyour boy girl dating talk at home before you come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能练过\NYeah, I probably do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.01,0:16:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你本书 若你那样有兴趣\NI'll give you a book if you're that interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,约会时\NOn dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,喷血时\NOn blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还有个医学问题？可能\NAnother medical question perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,没 我只觉得你是我见过的最漂亮的\NNo. I just think you're the prettiest thing I ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因为我四周黑麻麻地\NThat's because I'm sitting in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是美丽\Nyou're just beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,让路\NOut of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你得看好路再走\NYou need to watch where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我没想到你会介意\NI'm sorry. I didn't think you'd mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.67,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你没问过\NYou didn't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我想你可能会喜欢 - 就算我喜欢 你也要先问\N- I thought you might have liked it. - Well, I might have if you'd asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你来吗\NYou coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.73,0:18:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,走路小心点\NWatch where you're walking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何对我们只字不提\NWhy didn't you say nothing to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你会试着让我说出来\N'Cause you would have tried and talked me out of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亦知我做得对 - 那主的诫命呢\N- and I know what I'm doing is right. - And what about His Commandment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.48,0:19:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,在战争中那不是杀戮\NIt's not killing in a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我是保护 许多从我们教会入伍的男孩\NIt's protecting. Loads of boys from our church are going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗯 - 战事已起 他们要人\N- Yeah. - There is a war and they need men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在造纸厂上班救不了国\NAnd working in a paper mill ain't going to save this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来就像影星\NLooks like a movie star,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子\Nour boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,制服好看\NNice uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,帽子不错\Ngood hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,提醒了我 哈代穿这身制服是啥样\NReminds me of how Artie Giddens looked in his uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们奔赴法国\Nwhen we went to France.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.39,0:19:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得他吗？伯莎\NRemember him, Bertha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不要 汤姆 - 什么\N- Don't, Tom. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说哈尔穿起制服看着如何时髦\NI'm just saying how snappy Artie looked in his uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.74,0:19:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而所有的女孩似乎都这么认为\NAll you girls certainly seemed to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他使她们涌向他 他得意之极\NHe had them flocking to him. He was most proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望哈尔中枪时\NI just hope that when our Hal gets shot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是前面中枪\Nit's through the front of his jacket.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,干净利落 没痛苦\NLike a simple entry wound, not much mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,若是击中背部\NArtie got hit in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,把他的肠子 从前面出来落得到处都是\Nit blew most of his guts and intestines out his front, offal everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,彻底毁掉他的制服\NWrecked his uniform entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.96,0:20:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很幸运 他死了\NIt was lucky he was dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以他从不知他的制服看上去有多糟\Nso he never knew how awful his uniform looked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,离开我的视线\NGet outta of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我说难道你是山羊吗？\NWhat are you, part mountain goat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你不帮我吗？德斯蒙德·多斯\NAre you going to help me, Desmond Doss,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,或者你只想让我困住\Nor are you just going to leave me stranded?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你的 但你得付出代价\NI'll help you, but it's gonna cost you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,亲一个\NA kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.82,0:22:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这纯粹是敲诈 - 是的 女士\N- That is pure blackmail. - Well, yes, ma'am, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.89,0:22:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但那仍是我的条件\NBut that is still my condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.63,0:22:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是个交易\NThat's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我想抱着你亲\NAnd I'm going to hold you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.67,0:22:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NWell, hold on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.64,0:22:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会打我？是吗\NYou ain't gonna slap me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.83,0:22:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因我可能会带着你跟我掉下去\N'Cause I fall off, I'm going to take you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.60,0:22:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,吻我即知\NKiss me and find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.64,0:23:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我得参军\NI have to enlist.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.12,0:23:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能留在这儿而让他们都为我而战\NI can't stay here while all of them go fight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 你能 你能留在这儿 - 多萝西 我必须\N- Yes, you can. You can stay here. - Dorothy, I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.41,0:23:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要当军医\NI want to be a medic.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.03,0:23:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我指我是去救人而非杀人\NI figure I'll be saving people, not killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我得上班了 不想迟到\NI have to go to work. I'm going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,多萝西 别这样 多萝西 多萝西\NDorothy. Dorothy, darling. Dorothy. Dorothy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.76,0:23:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你想求我嫁给你还是别的\NSo are you going to ask me to marry you or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.55,0:24:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知你会否还讨厌我\NWell, I don't know. You still going to have me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知 你可没问\NWell, I wouldn't know, you haven't asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那 我来问你\NWell, I'm asking you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,全心全意地 你愿意嫁给我吗\Nwith all my heart and then some. Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那当然\NThen, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我愿意\NYes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.00,0:24:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,何时\NWhen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.45,0:24:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,待到你首次出征时\NSoon as you get your first leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.00,0:24:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但我此刻仍不喜欢你\NBut I still don't like you at this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.46,0:24:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.55,0:24:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好 - 好\N- Okay. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.56,0:24:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NWell, I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.00,0:24:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\NShh!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈说在这儿能见到你\NMomma said come see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.88,0:24:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.86,0:24:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这三位是我最好的朋友\NThese three were my best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.28,0:24:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起长大\NI grew up with 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.33,0:25:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,一起惹麻烦 一起追女生\NI got into trouble with 'em, chased girls with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.00,0:25:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起参军\NAnd I enlisted with 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.75,0:25:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,然后吾友们长眠于此\NNow my friends are there,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.38,0:25:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,泥草覆身 虫蛆啃噬\Ncovered in dirt and grass and eaten by worms.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.47,0:25:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想探望我孩子于此\NI don't want to have to visit my sons here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.08,0:25:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸我已签约\NDaddy, I signed up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.44,0:25:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我别无选择除了入伍 爸爸\NI couldn't do otherwise, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.86,0:25:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 人人都这样 - 你并非人人\N- Everybody else is doing... - You ain't everybody else!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.99,0:25:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,人人忙做事 不加思索 有如\NEverybody else jumps in and does things quick, without thinking! Like the
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.82,0:25:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这种该死的蠢货\NLike the damn idiot fools we were.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.98,0:25:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你可知活着的士兵所以活着 只因他们能思考\NAnd soldiers who live, they live because they can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.62,0:25:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能\NYou can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.91,0:25:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你得坐下思考 凡事祷告\NLook, you gotta sit and think and pray about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.90,0:25:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你 你现在就想想\NI mean, look at you, you're doing it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.72,0:25:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你无法靠自己活着 如果你去\NYou won't be able to live with yourself if you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.88,0:25:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我无法靠自己活着 假如我不去\NNo, I won't be able to live with myself if I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.17,0:25:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我要当个军医\NI'm going to be a medic.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.62,0:26:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那将是我服役的方式\NThat's going to be my way to serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.95,0:26:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就去把它想清楚\NSee, there you go, thinking it all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.16,0:26:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为这场战争会让你称心如意\NWhat, you figure this war is just going to fit in with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.00,0:26:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如你所愿\Nyour ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.44,0:26:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我只晓得我不怀疑这会很难\NWell, I don't doubt it's going to be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.57,0:26:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不是难 是不可能\NIt won't be hard, it'll be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.57,0:26:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 如今你那疯狂脑子里的信仰\NYou know, whatever beliefs you have in your crazy head now,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.45,0:26:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它们永不发生 不起作用\Nthey won't ever play out. It don't work that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.66,0:26:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,如有某些我所不知的奇遇 你活下来\NAnd if by some, I don't know, miracle chance you survive,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.04,0:26:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你不会把感谢给上帝\Nyou won't be giving no thanks to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.49,0:26:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 休息？- 休息下\N- Ready? - Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.42,0:26:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该走了\NY'all need some air.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.24,0:26:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 伙计们 迈迈腿 我理解\NCome on, fellas, shake a leg. Uncle Sam's got you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.59,0:26:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你得跟老妈说再见\NSay goodbye to Momma.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.74,0:26:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.10,0:26:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们 请离开公共汽车\NLadies, please, step away from the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.35,0:26:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我差点忘了\NI almost forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.35,0:26:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我非得找根撬棍吗？- 拿着\N- Do I need a crowbar? - Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.06,0:26:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你带上这个\NI want you to have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.98,0:26:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的\NIt's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.07,0:26:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它放在这儿\NYou keep it right here,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.34,0:26:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在那儿\Nwhere I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.95,0:27:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 再见 - 再见\N- Bye. - Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.10,0:27:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱你\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.67,0:28:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我非得盯着你的畸形吗？每次我走到床上\NDo I have to gaze at your deformity every time I walk to my bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.69,0:28:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,眼红吧 我的朋友\NGaze upon it in envy, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.97,0:28:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\NYou okay there?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.32,0:28:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你好象迷了路\NYou look lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.95,0:28:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,要不你就坐这儿\NVacancy right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.64,0:28:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不错的选择 那儿能从高山看到大湖\NWise choice. It's got views of the mountains down to the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.51,0:28:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,兰德尔·富勒\NRandall Fuller.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.03,0:28:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德·多斯\NDesmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.22,0:28:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他"教授" 你听不懂他说的每个字\NCall him "Teach."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.78,0:28:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,叫他"教授" 你听不懂他说的每个字\NNo one understands a word he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.53,0:28:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这儿没人懂\NThat's because no one else here can read.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.56,0:28:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那对睾丸的主人自称"好莱坞"\NThe testicles there belong to a man calling himself "Hollywood."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.70,0:28:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它们看起来更像是属于小家伙\NThey look like they belong to a smaller guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.63,0:28:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂睾丸\NYou know testicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.14,0:28:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 嘿 我刚买这双鞋\NOh! Hey, I just got these shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.00,0:28:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 呃 格雷斯·诺兰 来自雷德伍德 你呢\NHey, uh, Grease Nolan, outta Red Hook. Where you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.44,0:28:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 弗吉尼亚 - 威尔·比利哈\N- Virginia. - Ooh, hillbilly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.20,0:28:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你娶了你第一个表妹\NYou marry your first cousin?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.60,0:28:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,开个玩笑\NI'm just joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.93,0:28:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那边的史密提跟科恩斯基臭味相投\NThat's Smitty over there, whipping Kirzinski's ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.14,0:28:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好象你更牛？笨蛋\NLike you were doing any better, chowder head.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.64,0:28:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我可不想使你丢脸\NHey, I didn't want to embarrass you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.62,0:28:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,沃尔·科恩斯基 很高兴见到你\NWal Kirzinski, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.42,0:28:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 竹竿 你说你名字是啥？\NHey, beanpole, what did you say your name was?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.68,0:28:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德·多斯\NDesmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.99,0:29:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,边上那位是德克萨斯·刘易斯 当他是某类牛仔\NThat's Tex Lewis over there, he thinks he's some kind of cowboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.26,0:29:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有维托·雷诺利 他也许个小 但他可是斗牛犬\NAnd, uh, Vito Rinnelli. He may be small, but he is a bulldog.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.79,0:29:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嗨 - 你好吗？\N- Hey. - How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.99,0:29:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 德斯蒙德 - 噢\N- Desmond. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.83,0:29:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这位帅哥是幸运的福特 - 嘿\N- This handsome guy right here is Lucky Ford. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.75,0:29:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那边是沃克和皮尼克 他们自诩为洗牌手\NThat's Walker and Pinnick over there pretending they're card sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.87,0:29:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,安静 格雷斯 好吗\NPipe down, Grease, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.00,0:29:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你想被钱塞住嘴\NUnless you want to put your money where your mouth is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.01,0:29:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 嘿\NOh, hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.33,0:29:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这书\Nthe old
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.08,0:29:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不错吧\Ngood book, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.26,0:29:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得是 我觉得鲁西也有本好书\NI think... I think Lucky's got a good book.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.95,0:29:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧 鲁西\NRight, Lucky?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.23,0:29:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是本好书\NIt's a good read.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,立正\NAttention!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.87,0:29:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,列队 行动\NLine up! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.45,0:29:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一起来 行动 行动\NLet's go, move it. Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.93,0:30:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很怪\NYou are a very strange-looking individual
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.99,0:30:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你不介意我这样说吧？列兵\Nif you don't mind me saying so, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.98,0:30:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 姓名 - 安迪·沃克\N- Name? - Andy Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.21,0:30:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你死多久了？孩子\NHow long have you been dead, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.39,0:30:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我不是长官\N- Sir? - I am not "Sir"!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.51,0:30:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是豪厄尔中士或军士\NI am Sergeant Howell or Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.86,0:30:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"长官"是叫没用的人\N"Sir" you save for useless people.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.28,0:30:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你的名字是"食尸鬼"你说呢 - 沃克 中士\N- The name is "Ghoul," you say? - Walker, Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.77,0:30:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- "食尸鬼"是 - 是的 中士\N- Ghoul it is. - Yes, Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.44,0:30:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你的看上去有失常态 列兵\NThere's something off in your presentation, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.67,0:30:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,很难说\NCan't place it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.81,0:30:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的头发\NIs it your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.52,0:30:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你裤子上的皱纹\NIs it the wrinkle in your trousers?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.90,0:31:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我脚上插着刀 中士\NI have a knife in my foot, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.60,0:31:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 噢 是的 当然 是这把刀 - 不\N- Oh, yes, of course, that's it. The knife. - No,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.11,0:31:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你叫什么名字？士兵 - 史密提·瑞克\N- What is your name, soldier? - Smitty Ryker.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.70,0:31:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你的名字是"列兵白痴" 你可知为何\Nyour name is Private Idiot. Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.82,0:31:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 因为我脚上插着刀 - 谁会把刀插在哪儿？列兵\N- Because I have a knife in my foot. - Who placed the knife there, Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.79,0:31:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个意外 中士 我在练拉伸\NIt was an accident, Sarge. We was playing Stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.70,0:31:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,据我所知你不是有意插在那儿\NI am heartened by the knowledge you did not place it there with intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.92,0:31:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,谁扔的刀\NWho threw the knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.75,0:31:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 中士 列兵科恩斯基\NI did, Sergeant. Private Kirzinski.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.22,0:31:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是印地安部族 你属哪个部落？孩子\NYou look part Indian. To what tribe do you belong, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.88,0:31:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 我是波兰人 - 错\N- No, I'm Polish. - Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.09,0:31:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你一定有切诺基族或肖尼族血统\NI believe you must have Cherokee or Shawnee blood in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.56,0:31:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 长官 - 你在反驳我\N- No, Sergeant. - Are you contradicting me,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.35,0:31:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你这兔崽子 - 不 中士\N- you wagon-burning son of a bitch? - No, Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.10,0:31:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,让我见识下你的印第安战嚎孩子\NLet me see your Indian war cry, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.27,0:31:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会\NI don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.79,0:31:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大声些 让我看看\NLouder! Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.97,0:31:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你的动物图腾是啥\NWhat is your animal spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.80,0:31:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是乌梢蛇？\NAre you a garter snake?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.99,0:31:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 中士 - 你是花栗鼠？\N- No, Sergeant! - Are you a chipmunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.53,0:31:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 中士 - 你是跳舞的驯鹿？\N- No, Sergeant! - Are you a dancing reindeer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.08,0:31:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 中士 - 你在反驳我 中士？\N- No, Sergeant! - Are you contradicting me, Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.62,0:31:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 中士 - 好\N- No, Sergeant! - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.23,0:32:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那我从此叫你"酋长"\NThen I shall henceforth call you "Chief"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.68,0:32:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,作为向你族人致以崇高敬意的标识\Nas a sign of great respect to your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.23,0:32:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 中士\NThank you, Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.00,0:32:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你在咧嘴笑我孩子？还是你经常这样\NAre you grinning at me, boy, or is that your natural state?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.37,0:32:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不 中士\NNo, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.31,0:32:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 姓名 列兵 - 德斯蒙德·多斯\N- Name, Private? - Desmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.86,0:32:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过的玉米杆都都比你强得多\NI have seen stalks of corn with better physiques.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.72,0:32:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,搞得我想扯掉你的耳朵 列兵\NMakes me want to pull an ear off, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.12,0:32:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你能扛人吗？- 是 中士\N- Can you carry your weight? - Yes, Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.23,0:32:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是你这种重量的\NShould be easy for you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.42,0:32:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下士 - 中士\N- Corporal. - Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.61,0:32:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你要确保此人别被大风刮走\NMake sure you keep this man away from strong winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.90,0:32:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是 中士\NYes, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.60,0:32:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵"白痴"\NPrivate Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.71,0:32:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是 中士 - 把脚抬高\N- Yes, Sergeant. - Raise your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.91,0:32:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抬高点\NHigher.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.20,0:32:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,全部出去 马上\NEveryone outside. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.40,0:32:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来\NMove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.92,0:32:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我说了动起来\NI said move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.29,0:32:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我得穿制服 中士\NAll right. Just getting in my uniform, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.60,0:32:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我有叫他穿吗？下士 - 没有 中士\N- Did I ask him to, Corporal? - No memory of it, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.33,0:32:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信任何为自己自然裸露而如此骄傲的男人\NI believe any man who takes such pride in his natural naked state
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.01,0:32:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会享受户外的清爽\Nwill surely enjoy the brisk of the outdoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.48,0:32:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,现在放开你的私处 列兵帕兹\NNow move your privates, Private Parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.51,0:32:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,行动\NMove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.56,0:33:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,行动 你这个裸露崽子\NYou son of an exhibitionist!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.71,0:33:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我要教你们怎么结单套\NI am going to teach you how to tie a bowline knot,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.94,0:33:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你们能够把你的懒屁股从高处放下\Nso you can get your sorry asses down from a height,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.38,0:33:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好让我能踢它们\Nso I may then kick them!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.36,0:33:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,绕成一个圈\NCreate a loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.03,0:33:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这是兔子窝\NThis is the rabbit hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.53,0:33:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,兔子出了窝 绕着树子跑\NThe rabbit comes out of his hole, runs around the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.36,0:33:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,回到兔子窝\Ngoes back into the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.32,0:33:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,完成\NAll right,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.09,0:33:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一起做\Nlet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.25,0:33:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很好德克萨斯\NVery good, Tex.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.04,0:33:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,继续努力 "教授"\NKeep struggling, Teach.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.68,0:33:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没套过山羊吗 "好莱坞"\NHave you ever roped a goat, Hollywood?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.96,0:33:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,没有军士\NNo, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.74,0:33:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你从没瞪过山羊眼？\NHave you ever looked into a goat's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.68,0:33:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有 中士 - 好 那才不正常\N- No, Sarge. - Good, that would be unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.17,0:33:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂如不吸气必得死\NYou know if you don't breathe, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.64,0:33:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不错 列兵"白痴"\NGood, Private Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.35,0:33:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你老油条 你刚掉了五十英尺 摔断了脖子\NCongratulations, Greaseball, you just fell 50 feet and broke your neck!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.83,0:33:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,棒极了\NBrilliant,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.02,0:33:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵维托·雷诺利\NPrivate Vito Rinnelli.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.68,0:33:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你勒死自己毫无怜悯\NYou strangled yourself, numb nuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.80,0:33:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你是贝内利的粉丝\NAre you a fan of Benito?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.37,0:33:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不是 中士 - 有一点\N- No, Sergeant. - A bit taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.52,0:34:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是美国人 你会更高些\NIf you were American, you'd be taller.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.29,0:34:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么 多斯\NWhat've we got here, Doss,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.70,0:34:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,每个乳房各一个\None for each titty?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.68,0:34:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你是结单套 孩子\NYou were tying a bowline, boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.79,0:34:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不是结胸罩\Nnot building a bra!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.52,0:34:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有何可笑 下士？- 说不出来 中士\N- What is so funny, Corporal? - Couldn't tell you, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.42,0:34:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 来吧 娘们 爬起来 快 快\NCome on! Come on, ladies, pick it up! Move it! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.84,0:34:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,给我燃起来 快点\NI want to see some fire here. A little hustle.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.70,0:34:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,给我露几手\NShow me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.06,0:34:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,拼命跑\NRun like you mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.41,0:34:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下 下 下 更快 更快 更快 - 快 跑 跑\N- Down, down, down! Faster, faster! - Come on. Move it! Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.19,0:34:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去清洗地道 男孩们\NLet's go, it's bath time, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.21,0:34:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是时候洗洗了\NIt's bath time! trust you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.07,0:34:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,向前 向前 向前\NMove! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.99,0:34:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看到你赢 一起来\NI want to see you work. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.27,0:34:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,钻 钻 钻\NDig, dig, dig!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.72,0:34:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不要忘记耳后有人 一起来 快\NDon't forget behind your ears. Let's go. Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.68,0:34:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌你正享受这样 裸露狂\NI bet you're enjoying this, you naked degenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.21,0:34:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一起来 快点 快点 快点 动起来\NLet's go! Hustle. Hustle. Hustle. Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.16,0:34:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一起来 还等啥 一起来 把屁股搬起来\NLet's go! What are we waiting on? Let's go! Move your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.68,0:35:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,爬木头 翻墙壁 别跟废物亲近\NGet the wood! Get the wall! Don't get splinters!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.84,0:35:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,加油\NDrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.62,0:35:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,加油\NDrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.83,0:35:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 你没事吧？\NJeez, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.02,0:35:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事\NYeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.02,0:35:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- 打起精神来 小伙子们 走 - 快 走\N- Some spirit here, boys. Move! - Come on, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.56,0:35:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底啥毛病？不准休息\NWhat the hell is wrong with you? No one said take a rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.73,0:35:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股搬到终点线 快跑 快跑\NMove your asses to the finish line! Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.03,0:35:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点\NHustle! Hustle!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.99,0:35:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让你的屁股跨过该死的线\NGet your asses across that line!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 干得漂亮 多斯\NTime! Nice work, Doss!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.10,0:35:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这是美国政府给你们\NThis is a personal gift from the United States government
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.70,0:35:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,每一位的个人礼物\Nto each and every one of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.51,0:35:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,标准美式步枪 30口径 M1 加兰德步枪\NA standard issue U.S. rifle, caliber .30, M1,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.28,0:35:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,单配弹夹 肩射式半自动武器\Na clip-fed, shoulder-fired, semi-automatic weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.31,0:35:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,用于把死亡同毁灭带给敌人\Ndesigned to bring death and destruction to the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.42,0:35:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,它将成为你的爱侣\NThis is to be your lover,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.36,0:35:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你的情人\Nyour mistress
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.74,0:35:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你的小妾\Nyour concubine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.99,0:35:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是\NPerhaps
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.16,0:35:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是 你生命中唯一的真爱\Nthe only thing in life you will ever truly love.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.30,0:35:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们 一起来跳舞\NFellas, let's dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.23,0:36:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,挑个女孩\NGrab a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.65,0:36:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不要把枪对着前方\NDon't point your gun forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.53,0:36:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天不想中弹\NI do not want to be shot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.82,0:36:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你多么心痒\NNo matter how much you are tempted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.21,0:36:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,把枪放侧边\NPlace the weapon by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.21,0:36:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,立正\NPay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.22,0:36:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗 列兵"玉米杆"\NProblem, Private Corn Stalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.03,0:36:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,尺寸不对\NIs there not one in your size,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.05,0:36:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还是颜色有问题\Nor is it the color that is the issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.96,0:36:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不 中士\NNo, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.97,0:36:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我被告知我不必携带武器\NI was... I was told I don't have to carry a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.48,0:36:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,上前一步列兵 我没听清\NCome again? Step forward, Private. I can't be hearing this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.12,0:36:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 中士\NWell, I'm sorry, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.54,0:36:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能碰枪\NI can't touch a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.25,0:36:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟是什么问题\NWhat exactly is the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.06,0:36:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没有问题 只是误会\NNo problem, just a mistake, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.85,0:36:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我参军时就说过 这不可能\NI told the Army when I joined up. That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.17,0:37:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你可知为何不可能 列兵\NDo you know why it's not possible, Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.51,0:37:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不 长官\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.20,0:37:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为美军不会犯错\NBecause the United States Army does not make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.22,0:37:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,若有问题\NSo if there's a problem, .
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.35,0:37:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,若有问题 你就是那问题\Nyou must be that problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.52,0:37:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我从没想过被派到步兵连\NI was just never supposed to be sent to a rifle company.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.87,0:37:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个"CO" 长官\NHe's a C.O., sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.32,0:37:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个"拒服兵役者"\NYou're a conscientious objector,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.27,0:37:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,而你参了军\Nand you joined the Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.49,0:37:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 先生\NWell, no, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.83,0:37:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个"尽责的合作者"\NI'm a conscientious cooperator.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.62,0:37:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你在愚弄我？多斯 - 不 不 先生 我自愿\N- Are you screwing with me, Doss? - No. No, sir. I volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.71,0:37:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿制服没问题\NI ain't got no problem with wearing my uniform,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.46,0:37:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,向国旗行礼 尽我的义务\Nor saluting the flag and doing my duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.77,0:37:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,只是\NIt's just
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.09,0:37:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,只是不可以拿枪杀人\Njust carrying a gun and the taking of human life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.05,0:37:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你不杀人？\NYou don't kill?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.81,0:37:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 就这些 - 是的 先生 就这些\N- That's all. - Yes, sir, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.60,0:37:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你知战争中杀戮确实很多\NYou know quite a bit of killing does occur in a war?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.78,0:37:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.43,0:37:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 战争的本质\NI mean, that is the essential nature of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.71,0:37:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是 长官\NYes, sir. .
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.92,0:37:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.00,0:38:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你对美军还有任何其它要求吗\NDo you have any other requirements of the United States Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.39,0:38:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么我们可以做 以确保\NIs there anything else that we can do to ensure
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.98,0:38:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你会满意地跟我们一起呆这儿\Nthat you have a comfortable stay here with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.86,0:38:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想在周六工作 长官\NHe doesn't want to work on Saturdays, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.63,0:38:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 周六是\NWell, Saturdays...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.10,0:38:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是"基督复临安息日"者 因此\NI'm a Seventh-day Adventist. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.54,0:38:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,周六是我的安息日 那就不允许我工作\NSaturday is my Sabbath, so I'm not allowed to work then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.12,0:38:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不认为这会带来问题 你呢？中士\NI don't think that poses a problem, do you, Sergeant?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.90,0:38:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应要求敌人别在安息日进攻\NWe shall simply ask the enemy not to invade on the Sabbath,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.45,0:38:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为列兵多斯在此祈祷\N'cause Private Doss here is at prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.30,0:38:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.54,0:38:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们搞清楚了\NNow we got that clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.34,0:38:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在让我告诉你我的要求 它们不像\NNow let me tell you my requirements.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.35,0:38:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你的那么复杂 它们极简单\NThey're not as complicated as yours. They're very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.81,0:38:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只要你一直呆在这个连队里 由我指挥\NAs long as you're in this company, under my command,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.92,0:38:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你就得服从我的命令 句号\Nyou will obey my orders. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.85,0:38:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你若在此做不到 我不信你在战斗能做到\NIf you can't do it here, I can't trust you to do it in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.25,0:38:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把你视为符合"第八条例"\NI'm putting you in for a Section 8,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.08,0:38:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"我会让你免役\Npsychiatric discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.10,0:38:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,解散\NDismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.99,0:38:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,先生们\NGentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.01,0:39:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你们见见列兵德斯蒙德·多斯\NI want you to meet Private Desmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.84,0:39:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,显然地\NApparently,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.41,0:39:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,显然地 列兵多斯不相信暴力\NPrivate Doss does not believe in violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.15,0:39:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他不愿实施暴力\NHe does not practice violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.09,0:39:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他甚至不屑摸枪\NHe will not even deign to touch a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.22,0:39:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,要知道 列兵多斯\NYou see, Private Doss
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.34,0:39:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是一个"拒服兵役者"\Nis a conscientious objector.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.04,0:39:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我恳请你们\NSo I plead with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.91,0:39:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别指望他在战场上拯救你\Ndo not look to him to save you on the battlefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.71,0:39:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他无疑会\Nbecause he will undoubtedly
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.09,0:39:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,太忙于跟他的良心搏斗\Nbe too busy wrestling with his conscience
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.96,0:39:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,去协助\Nto assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.53,0:39:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- 中士 那不是真的 中士 - 列兵 别解释了\N- Sarge, that's not true. - Private, as you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.18,0:39:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你们中有些人对此很有意见\NNow, I realize some of you might have strong feelings about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.70,0:39:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是男人为何而战\NIt is what we men fight for.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.16,0:39:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为了捍卫权利\NTo defend our rights,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.24,0:39:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为了保护妇女和儿童\Nand to protect our women and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.04,0:39:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,即使列兵多斯的信念\NEven if Private Doss' beliefs
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.90,0:39:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可能会导致妇女和儿童死亡\Nmight cause women and children to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.15,0:39:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我希望本连队的每个人\NSo I will expect everyone in this company
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.55,0:39:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,给予列兵多斯 充分尊重他应有的尊重\Nto give Private Doss the full measure of respect he is due
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.04,0:39:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为短时间内 他将与我们同在\Nfor the short time he will be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.18,0:40:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,清楚了吗\NAm I clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.78,0:40:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 中士\NYes, Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.45,0:40:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你拿的是啥 多斯\NWhat'cha got there, Dessie?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.14,0:40:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道那是什么吗？像是袖珍版\NYou know what that is. It just seems kind of small.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.29,0:40:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,专门给不完整的男人吧\NIt's half the Bible for half the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.00,0:40:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看彼得份上 史密提 把圣经还给他\NFor Pete's sake, Smitty, give him back his Bible.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.69,0:40:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我没跟你说\NI don't remember speaking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.57,0:40:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你为何不打架\NSo, how come you don't fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.62,0:40:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你自以为比我们优秀\NYou think you're better than us?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.13,0:40:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.82,0:40:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 如果你被攻击 怎么办\NWhat if you was attacked?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.81,0:40:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢吗\NSay, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.39,0:40:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,圣经说 你要转过另一边脸\NThe Bible says to turn the other cheek, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.74,0:40:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,看见没？跟信仰无关 伙计们\NSee, I don't think this is a question of religion, fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.08,0:40:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为是懦弱\NI think this is cowardice,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.50,0:40:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,显而易见\Nplain and simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.03,0:40:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 多斯？\NIs that right, Doss?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.24,0:41:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你娘炮？是吗\NAre you chickenshit, that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.91,0:41:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,来啊\NGo on,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.76,0:41:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来打\Ntake a poke.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.34,0:41:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那好 我不还手\NTell you what, I'm going to give you a free shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.02,0:41:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那儿\NRight there.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.42,0:41:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,打我 多斯\NHit me, Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.71,0:41:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,来\NGo on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.18,0:41:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 啥毛病 - 上啊\N- Let him have it. - Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.64,0:41:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不打？\NNo?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.72,0:41:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,娘炮\NChickenshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.44,0:41:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 这是什么？\NHold on here. What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.48,0:41:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,把它给我\NGive me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.08,0:41:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这娘们好看 - 漂亮\N- This is a fine-looking broad. - Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.24,0:41:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 让大伙看一下\NHey, pass it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.82,0:41:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,如今这种娘们\NNow, this would be the kind of broad
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.51,0:41:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的男人才配得上\Nthat deserves a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.47,0:41:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,把它还给我\NGive me that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.84,0:41:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,请\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.69,0:41:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,请\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.40,0:41:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,请把它归还 史密提\N"Please give it back, Smitty."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.04,0:41:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,请把它归还 史密提\NPlease give it back, Smitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.31,0:42:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你听得到声音？德斯蒙德\NDo you hear voices, Desmond?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.56,0:42:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不 长官\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.34,0:42:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解为上帝在跟你说话？是那样吗\NBut I understand that God talks to you. Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.90,0:42:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我没疯\NSir, I'm not a crazy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.89,0:42:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,那你觉得大多数人怎么看你\NIs that how you feel most people regard you,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.40,0:42:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,疯子\Na crazy person?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.70,0:42:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不同别人我知道 只是\NI'm different. I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.52,0:42:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我不愿弄虚作假\NI'm not going to pretend to be something I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.50,0:42:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是我\NI am what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.07,0:42:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来很孤独\NSounds lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.19,0:42:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你孤独吗\NYou lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.40,0:42:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那么 你听不到声音 -不 长官\N- So, you don't hear voices. - No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.79,0:42:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我向上帝祷告\NI pray to God
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.76,0:42:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我还觉得他能听见 只是那并非交谈\Nand I like to think He hears me, but it ain't a conversation,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.74,0:42:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就像此刻我绝不会假装我们得谈谈\Nlike the one we're pretending to have right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.57,0:42:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 假装？列兵 - 是 长官\N- Pretending, Private? - Well, yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.35,0:42:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你的打算干嘛 说我是"第八条例者"\NI know all you really want to do is give me a Section 8,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把我撵出部队 只是\Ndrum me out of the Army, but
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.11,0:42:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是\NI'm not off
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.74,0:42:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,神明在上\Nup above.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.75,0:42:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是信我所信\NI just simply believe what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.66,0:42:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我尽量去理解\NWell, I'm trying to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.56,0:43:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗？\Nall right?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.20,0:43:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是上帝叫你别拿枪\NWas it God who told you not to pick up a rifle?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.50,0:43:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝说勿杀人\NGod says not to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.56,0:43:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那是他的最重要的戒律之一\NThat's one of His most important Commandments.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.27,0:43:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数人把此理解为别谋杀\NMost people take that to mean, "Don't commit murder."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.14,0:43:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,战争是完全不同的情况\NWar is a completely different set of circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.38,0:43:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,耶稣说\NJesus said,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.73,0:43:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我把一个新的命令给你们\N"A new Commandment I give unto you,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.17,0:43:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,即你爱别人 有如我爱你\Nthat you love one another, just as I have loved you."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.19,0:43:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正在跟撒旦作战\NThis is Satan himself we're fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.27,0:43:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是\NSurely,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.04,0:43:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,虔诚的基督徒 你看得出来\Nas a good Christian, you can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.93,0:43:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我看得出 长官 这也是我参军的原因\NI can see that, sir, and that is why I joined up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.49,0:43:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很抱歉 我不能带武器\NBut I'm sorry, I will not bear arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.47,0:43:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他的宗教观确实独一无二 但这些\NHis religious views are certainly unique,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.07,0:43:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不违反第八条例的免役范畴\Nbut they do not constitute grounds for a Section 8 discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.87,0:43:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我该如何让这样的人听命于我\NHow am I supposed to maintain discipline with a man like that in my unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.88,0:43:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.37,0:43:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,但他是一个合法的"拒服兵役者"\NBut he is a legitimate conscientious objector,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.74,0:43:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,他必须被允许作为"军医"提供\Nand he must be allowed to work as a combat medic,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.10,0:43:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他有资格在所有其它区域进行训练\Nprovided he qualifies in all other areas of his training.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.02,0:44:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们可帮助缓和他的想法\NPerhaps we could help make believe in his idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.71,0:44:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好 你把他关在兵营去KP\NYeah, you restrict him to barracks and KP.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.31,0:44:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他扔上帝给你 你扔地狱砸他\NIf he throws God at you, you throw hell right at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.92,0:44:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我要他消失\NI want him gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.40,0:44:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,多斯\NDoss, your area is a disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.60,0:44:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个猪圈\NIt's a pig sty!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.04,0:44:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- 有何可笑 瑞克？- 不 中士\N- Something funny, Ryker? - No, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.74,0:44:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你脑子进大粪了？- 不 中士\N- You got some shit on your mind? - No, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.82,0:44:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没意识到的\NWhat you men fail to recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.88,0:44:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就是一只队伍并不会比它的最弱者更强\Nis a unit is no better than its weakest member!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.72,0:44:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你们记住这教训\NNow, to help you learn that lesson,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.73,0:44:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,本周末不准休息\Nthere will be no passes this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.25,0:44:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,全部去KP\NYou will all be on KP!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.74,0:44:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在全体全速徒步20英里\NRight now, everybody in full gear for a 20-mile hike.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.32,0:44:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去 一起去\NLet's go! Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.70,0:45:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,保持头脑清醒\NGet your heads right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.74,0:45:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不要自怜\NDon't start feeling sorry for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.03,0:45:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的自怜样叫我恶心\NMakes me sick see you feel sorry for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.20,0:45:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些狗不知累为何物\NYou dogs don't know what tired is.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.80,0:45:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会继续跑直到我倒下\NWe're going to keep going till I drop.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.46,0:45:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 伙计们\NCome on guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.51,0:45:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 住手 别打了 去睡觉\NHey, knock it off. Trying to sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.77,0:45:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 离我远点 滚开 - 好 好\N- Get off me. Get off me. - Okay. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.07,0:45:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你还在这里\NWhy the hell are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.31,0:45:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 立正 - 原地别动\N- Attention - As you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.26,0:46:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,多斯在哪儿\NWhere's Doss?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.65,0:46:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你不好 伙计\NThis isn't good for anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.46,0:46:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 我参军不是想这样\NSure ain't what I joined up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.99,0:46:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这跟你为何参军无关\NIt's not about what you joined up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.20,0:46:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有关在此诸位的命\NIt's about the lives of every man in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.83,0:46:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,及你的命 孩子\NAnd yours, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.21,0:46:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候退出了\NIt's time to quit this.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.09,0:46:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,穿好衣服 我送你\NFinish getting dressed and I'll walk you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.43,0:46:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 多斯\NIt's okay, Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.64,0:46:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,别为此羞愧\NThere's no shame in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.96,0:47:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.08,0:47:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我有额外的执勤 今天 上午我得去KP 所以\NI got extra guard duty today, and I'm on KP this morning, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.05,0:47:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能\NCan't.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.38,0:47:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 多斯\NAll right, Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.23,0:47:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵多斯\NPrivate Doss,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.85,0:47:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你能认出打你的人吗\Ncan you identify the men that beat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.17,0:47:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不 中士\NNo, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.94,0:47:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说你不知道是谁打了你\NAre you saying that you don't know who attacked you?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.20,0:47:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未说过我被打了 中士\NI never said I was attacked, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.70,0:47:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你究竟在说啥？多斯\NWell, what the hell are you saying, Doss?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.63,0:47:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你伤得难以入睡\NYou bruised half your body sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.96,0:48:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我睡得很沉\NI... I sleep pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.68,0:48:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAlright.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.68,0:48:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,本周计划湿训 确保你戴上帽子\NIf you plan on getting wet this weekend, make sure you put on a hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.33,0:48:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,下一个\NNext.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.46,0:48:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我不希望任何人回来尿在奶油里\NDon't want anyone coming back pissing cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.93,0:48:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是想要咖啡吗？中士\NWhat, you don't want none for your coffee, Sarge?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.47,0:48:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,给你颗枪子儿如何？史密提\NHow about a shot right now, Smitty?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.16,0:48:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- 讲讲经验 中士 - 下一个\N- You speaking from experience, Sarge? - Next.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.94,0:48:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你得问你娘 老油条\NYou'd have to ask your mom about that, Greaseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.82,0:48:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,稍息\NAt ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.61,0:48:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵多斯\NPrivate Doss,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.67,0:48:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕我不能准你的假\NI'm afraid I can't authorize your pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.55,0:48:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,假期只给通过基本训练的人\NThis is a furlough for men who have passed the basic training.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.00,0:48:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,尊敬的长官 我过了\NWell, sir, respectfully, sir, I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.38,0:48:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我申请了此假 三周前 我要结婚\NI put in for this furlough three weeks ago. I'm getting married
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.48,0:48:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,今天下午\Nthis afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.69,0:48:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你步枪不合格\NIt says you're not rifle qualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.72,0:49:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要携带步枪 长官 上校施特尔策 他\NWell, I'm not required to carry a rifle, sir. Colonel Stelzer, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.64,0:49:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上校施特尔策规定：\NColonel Stelzer's determination was...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.86,0:49:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,特许多斯作为军医服役\N"Doss must be allowed to work as a combat medic,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.70,0:49:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,准予他有资格在任何其它区域完成训练\Nprovided he qualifies in all other areas of his training."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.31,0:49:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而你在枪械上无资格 列兵\NAnd you have not qualified on the rifle range, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.10,0:49:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很清楚\NPretty clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.20,0:49:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,给我演示下你会拿枪\NShow me you know how to handle a rifle
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.11,0:49:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我就准假\Nand I'll sign your furlough.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.45,0:49:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 下士坎农 - 长官\N- Corporal Cannon. - Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.34,0:49:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,给列兵多斯你的枪\NHand Private Doss your firearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.07,0:49:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不会碰步枪 长官- 我不是要求你 列兵\N- I won't touch a rifle, sir. - I'm not asking you, Private!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.32,0:49:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个部队指挥官的直接命令\NThat is a direct order from a company commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.90,0:49:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,看上帝份上 多斯\NFor God's sake, Doss,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.03,0:49:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,别再废话 退出\Nyou stop this nonsense and quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.43,0:49:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,拒绝\NRefuse,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.11,0:49:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我则没有追索权 只能送你去军事法庭\Nand I will have no recourse but to court-martial you,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.46,0:50:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你将在军事监狱度过战争期\Nand you will spend the duration of the war in a military prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.61,0:50:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能 长官\NI can't, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.35,0:50:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意等多久 多萝西\NHow much longer would you like to wait, Dorothy?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.51,0:50:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我想得足够久\NI think it's been long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.92,0:50:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是太遗憾了\NI'm so very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.98,0:50:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有时男人会临阵退缩\NSometimes men just get cold feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.44,0:50:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,有的男人会有\NSome men might.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.04,0:50:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但我的德斯蒙德不会\NNot my Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.38,0:51:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能觉得我真是个混蛋\NYou probably think I'm a real son of a bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.40,0:51:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,只在乎规定不关心自己人\Nwho cares only about regulations and not his men.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.37,0:51:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.35,0:51:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟任何人一样信任此书\NI believe in this book as much as any man.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.25,0:51:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,跟任何人一样\NAnd just like any man,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.68,0:51:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我会被良心困扰\NI wrestle with my conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.01,0:51:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,但当世上你珍视的一切皆受摧残 你会怎做？\Nbut what do you do when everything you value in this world is under attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.75,0:51:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 长官\NI don't know, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.86,0:51:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我没法回答那种深刻的问题\NI ain't got answers to questions that big,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.33,0:51:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但我感同我价值观也在饱受摧残\Nbut I also feel like my values are under attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.08,0:51:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知何故\Nand I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.86,0:51:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不关心你的原则 因为日本人不在乎\NI don't give a rat's ass about your principles because the Japs don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.73,0:51:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果日本女人攻击你\NIf one of them attacks you and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.26,0:51:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,受伤的士兵 你怎么办\Nsome wounded soldier, what are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.92,0:51:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,用你的圣经揍他\NHit him with your Bible?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.29,0:52:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我已准备好为大家牺牲\NI'm prepared to give my life for my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.49,0:52:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你无法赢得战争即使你牺牲\NYou don't win wars by giving up your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.12,0:52:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧\NLook,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.44,0:52:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧 我只身到此 因我不愿看到你烂在牢房\NI'm only here because I don't want to see you rotting in a prison cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.04,0:52:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,认罪 为自己争取法庭怜悯\NPlead guilty, throw yourself at the mercy of the court.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.81,0:52:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他们会让你回家祈祷\NMaybe they'll let you go home and pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.55,0:52:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,让勇士们去赢得战争\NLet the brave men out there go and win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.98,0:52:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不能说服你\NIf I can't convince you,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.32,0:52:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她可以\Nmaybe she can.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.61,0:52:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不准我打电话你\NThey wouldn't let me call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.48,0:52:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道不是你不打\NI knew it wasn't your making.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.66,0:52:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他们对你做了些啥\NWhat have they done to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.04,0:52:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 我很好\NIt's okay, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.58,0:52:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只是打了几下墙还有些失落\NI just went a couple of rounds with the wall and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.96,0:52:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说你会入狱 德斯蒙德\NThey're saying you could go to prison, Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.46,0:52:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至更糟\NLeavenworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.48,0:52:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一定有别的办法\NThere must be some other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.51,0:53:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知将会怎样\NI don't know what that could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.41,0:53:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了他们要求的每件事 除了这件事\NI've done everything they asked me, except this one thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.45,0:53:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一直待我如罪犯 只因我不愿杀敌\Nand I'm being treated like a criminal just 'cause I won't kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.25,0:53:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你尽了力\NYou tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.85,0:53:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没人否认\NNobody can say you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.60,0:53:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但你在狱中能救谁\NBut who are you going to save in prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.97,0:53:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,可能没人\NProbably nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.88,0:53:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为何不拿起笨枪 四处挥挥\NThen why can't you just pick up the stupid gun and wave it around?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.88,0:53:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不必用枪 只需带枪\NYou don't have to use it, just meet them halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.41,0:53:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我不能那样做 - 是的 你能 这只是骄傲\N- I can't do that. - Yes, you can. It's just pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.78,0:53:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,骄傲跟倔强 别把你的意志跟上帝的混同\NPride and stubbornness. Don't confuse your will with the Lord's.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.03,0:53:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直很骄傲\NHave I been prideful?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.59,0:53:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我真的很骄傲\NMaybe I am prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.60,0:53:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知 我怎能独自活着\NBut I don't know how I'm going to live with myself
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.70,0:53:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,若不忠于我之所信\Nif I don't stay true to what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.15,0:53:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看着我们你怎能跟我一起活下去\NMuch less how you could live with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.57,0:54:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我想做个男人 如你所见\NI'd never be the man that I want to be in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.45,0:54:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱上你\NI fell in love with you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.01,0:54:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因你不象其他人\Nbecause you weren't like anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.94,0:54:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不会想那样\Nand you didn't try to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.17,0:54:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,任何时刻都别认为你会让我失望\NDo not think for one moment that you will disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.43,0:54:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我将爱你\NI will love you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.59,0:54:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎样\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.49,0:54:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知他要做啥\NI don't know what he's gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.77,0:54:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他输定了 无论如何\NHe loses no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.53,0:54:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想让他认罪\NThey want him to plead guilty,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.76,0:54:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但这会让他开除军籍\Nbut then he'll get a dishonorable discharge.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.49,0:54:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,否则他就是违抗他们 他必会入狱\NOtherwise he fights them, and he for sure goes to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.22,0:55:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,无论怎样 他们会叫他懦夫\NEither way, they'll call him a coward
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.65,0:55:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我看不出他怎能那样活着\Nand I don't see how he can live with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.86,0:55:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 多萝西\NWell, thank you, Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.24,0:55:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能跟他谈谈\NIf you get to talk to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.58,0:55:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他我们爱他 会为他祈祷\Ntell him that we love him and that we're praying for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.90,0:55:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,会为你们祈祷\NWe're praying for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.88,0:55:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我会的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.55,0:55:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜\NBye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.36,0:55:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,汤姆 你疯了 你神志不清了\NTom, you're out of your mind, you're delirious.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.24,0:55:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然失去了理智\NOf course, I'm out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.83,0:55:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我是谁 我疯了\NWhat do you think I am? I'm out of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.70,0:55:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,请你离开这屋\NYou leave this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.66,0:55:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 汤姆 把它放下\NNo, Tom! Put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.33,0:55:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放开我 婆娘 - 嘿\N- Get away from me, woman! - Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:11.98,0:56:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,有何贵干 先生\NMay I help you, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.32,0:56:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想找准将穆斯格罗夫\NI wish to speak to Brigadier General Musgrove.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.28,0:56:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,没有预约可不行 那样绝无可能\NNot without an appointment you can't. That would be quite impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.42,0:56:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如能劳你告诉他：\NUh, if you would kindly tell him
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.46,0:56:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,下士托马斯·多斯将感激一个简短的面谈\NCorporal Thomas Doss would appreciate a brief word.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.51,0:56:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他在开非常重要的会\NHe's in a very important meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.53,0:56:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟他在法国贝洛伍德打过仗 他是我队长\NI fought with him in France at Belleau Wood. He was my captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.22,0:56:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,求您女士 此事至关重要\NPlease, ma'am, it's most vital.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.17,0:56:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 女士\NThank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.20,0:56:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,门外有个人 托马斯·多斯\NThere's a man out there, Tom Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.95,0:56:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,多斯？\NDoss?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.42,0:57:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,仅需一分钟\NBe over in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.58,0:57:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你将安全到家 就跟没事一样\NYou'll be home safe and sound, like nothing ever happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.63,0:58:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是列兵多斯的听证会\NThis is a hearing into the matter of Private Desmond Doss.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.94,0:58:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,指控是他违反了其指挥官的\NThe charge is disobeying a series of direct orders
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.71,0:58:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一系列直接命令 被告怎么说\Nfrom his commanding officer. How says the defendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.84,0:58:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵多斯希望进行无罪答辩\NPrivate Doss wishes to enter a "not guilty" plea.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.81,0:58:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗 列兵？我以为已同意过\NIs that so, Private? I thought this was agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.70,0:58:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你想进行某种讨价还价的答辩？\NYou wanted to enter some sort of plea bargain.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.08,0:58:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是的 长官 但我改变了主意 - 就这样？\N- Yes, sir, but I changed my mind. - Just like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.54,0:58:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望进行军事诉讼\NYou wish to proceed to a court-martial?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.11,0:58:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.65,0:58:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那你如愿了列兵\NWell, on your head, then, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.73,0:58:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,开始\NProceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.01,0:58:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,法官大人\NYour Honor,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.38,0:58:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵多斯挥舞其道德观\NPrivate Doss waves his morality at us
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.38,0:58:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,有如某种荣誉的徽章\Nlike it's some kind of badge of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.56,0:58:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他炫耀他的蔑视 直接违反其指挥官的\NHe flaunts his contempt by directly disobeying a series of direct orders
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.31,0:58:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一系列直接命令\Nfrom his commanding officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.57,0:58:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,当这些最优秀的年轻人牺牲自己性命抵御邪恶时\NWhen the very best of our young men are sacrificing their lives against...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.28,0:58:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你没事吧？- 是的\N- You okay? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.95,0:58:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他们还在审议？- 是的 先生\N- Are they still deliberating? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.37,0:59:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你把这个拿进去\NOkay, now you go take this in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.37,0:59:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能 必须是军人\NI can't. It's strictly military personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.25,0:59:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那你让他们中某个带进去 - 他们不会帮忙\N- Well, then you get one of them to take it in. - They ain't out to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.49,0:59:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就等着埋了他\NThey're fixing to bury him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.23,0:59:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,任何军事法院只需问被告一个问题：\NThere is only one question that any military court need ask of the accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.69,0:59:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你否认违反上校萨斯顿的直接命令\NDo you deny disobeying Colonel Sangston's direct orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.22,0:59:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 你否认吗？列兵\NWell, do you, Private?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.92,0:59:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不 长官 我不否认 - 那你为何要质疑它呢\N- No, sir. I don't. - Why are you contesting it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.90,0:59:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这对你为何如此重要 使你拒绝去 触摸武器\NWhy is it so important to you, given your refusal to even touch a weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.18,0:59:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是在部队中服役\Nto serve in a combat unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.93,0:59:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因为当日本偷袭珍珠港之时 我视为针对我个人\NBecause when the Japanese attacked Pearl Harbor, I took it personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.31,0:59:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识的每个人都愤然参军 包括我\NEveryone I knew was on fire to join up, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.74,0:59:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,有两个人在我们镇上\NThere were two men in my home town...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.61,0:59:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,被判4F不合格\Ndeclared 4-F unfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.91,0:59:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们就自杀了 因为不能服役\NThey killed themselves because they couldn't serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.38,1:00:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,为何？我在国防工厂有份工作 我可以续约\NI had a job in a defense plant and I could've taken a deferment,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.51,1:00:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,但那样不对\Nbut that ain't right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.45,1:00:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不对：别人就该去战斗去牺牲\NIt isn't right that other men should fight and die,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.95,1:00:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,而我只是安全的呆坐屋里\Nthat I would just be sitting at home safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.15,1:00:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要服役\NI need to serve.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.44,1:00:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我有能力有激情作为军医服役\NI got the energy and the passion to serve as a medic.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.37,1:00:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,应当在其他伙伴当中 毫无危害 只是\NRight in the middle with the other guys. No less danger, just...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.04,1:00:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,当每个人都在取命 我是去救命\NWhile everybody else is taking life, I'm going to be saving it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.58,1:00:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这世界已把自己搞得四分五裂\NWith the world so set on tearing itself apart,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.07,1:00:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这对我不算是太糟糕的事\Nit doesn't seem like such a bad thing to me
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.96,1:00:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,去把那些碎片重聚一块儿\Nto want to put a little bit of it back together.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.43,1:00:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.90,1:00:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉先生 无人准进\NSorry, sir, nobody's allowed to go...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.51,1:00:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你不知 我儿就是被告\NNo, you don't understand. My son is the defendant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.68,1:00:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我理解 先生 但是无人准进 - 我有封信\N- I understand, sir, but nobody's allowed... - I have information
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.32,1:00:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- 非常重要 - 先生 你不可以进去\N- that's important. - Sir, you are not allowed...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.69,1:00:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 表达的情感值得称赞\NWhile the sentiments expressed are laudable,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.69,1:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,指控的事实无可争辩\Nthe facts of the charge seem incontestable, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.90,1:00:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那边所为何事\NWhat the hell is going on out there?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.76,1:01:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,让他进来\NLet him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.27,1:01:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是一战制服 - 是的 长官\N- That's a Great War uniform. - It is, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.68,1:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我得请您过目此信 恕我直言\NSir, I need to show you this. With respect, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.83,1:01:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 您不再是军人\Nyou are no longer a member of the military.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.04,1:01:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能参加此审议 我很遗憾\NYou are unable to attend this hearing. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.99,1:01:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说真是这样的了\NIs that truly the way it works, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.05,1:01:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你为国而战 你失去了无数挚爱\NYou fight for your country, you lose so much that was dear to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.11,1:01:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就没用了\Nand then you're done with?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.18,1:01:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没人认得你的制服了 所以无权发声\NThe uniform is forgotten. You have no voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.27,1:01:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你参战了里昂战役？\NYou were at Lys?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.67,1:01:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官 在贝洛森林\NI was, sir. And at Belleau Wood.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.86,1:01:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,两次授勋 我看到的 先生\NTwice decorated, I see. Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.40,1:01:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你是被告之父\NI take it you are the Private's father.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.00,1:01:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我是 长官 托马斯·多斯\NI am, sir. Thomas Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.87,1:01:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那么作为前军人 你知这儿有法律\NThen, as a former military man, you know there are laws here...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.15,1:01:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 我清楚法律 我是 我知我儿受这些法律保护\NSir, I know the law and I know my son is protected by those laws.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.41,1:01:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,它们受宪法约束\NThey are framed in our constitution.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.95,1:01:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信它们 像他那样\NAnd I believe in them, as he does.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.03,1:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是为何我曾为捍卫它们而战\NThey are why I went and fought to protect them.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.51,1:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是我所思所为\NAt least, that is what I thought I was doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.66,1:02:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果不是为此\NBecause if it wasn't for that,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.90,1:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不知我到底去那里干了啥 长官\Nthen I have no idea what the hell I was doing there, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.72,1:02:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 下士多斯\NThank you, Corporal Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.01,1:02:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看这信\NLet me have the letter.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.32,1:02:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你得离开\NYou must go.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.29,1:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,被告作为一个"拒服兵役者"的权利\N"The defendant's rights as a conscientious objector
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.73,1:02:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,受国会一项法案的保护\Nare protected by an Act of Congress
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.76,1:02:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他不能被迫放弃这些权利\Nand he cannot be compelled to waive those rights.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.80,1:02:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,权利包括本案述及之违抗携带武器命令\NThat includes, in this case, his disobeying orders to bear arms."
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.17,1:02:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,签署 准将穆斯格罗夫\NSigned, Brigadier General Musgrove,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.02,1:02:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,战争服务指挥官 华盛顿特区\NWar Services Commander, Washington, D.C.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.95,1:02:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,上校\NColonel?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.32,1:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我撤销控诉 - 那么本案驳回\N- I withdraw the charges, sir. - Then this case is dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.06,1:03:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵多斯 你可自由的投入战斗的地狱烈火\NPrivate Doss, you are free to run into the hellfire of battle
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.24,1:03:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,无需任何武器保护自己\Nwithout a single weapon to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.14,1:03:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你可恢复原职责\NYou may resume your duties
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.21,1:03:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,作为军医开始训练\Nand begin training as a combat medic.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.38,1:03:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他去哪儿了？- 走了 出来就走\N- Where is he? - Gone. Straight after.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.63,1:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我请求他留下 说他同样想留下 - 好 我明白\N- I begged him to stay. I told him you'd want to see him. - No, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.93,1:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你回家后告诉他：我爱他 - 好的\N- When you get home, you tell him I love him. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.13,1:03:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.17,1:04:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你要好好的回到我身边\NYou better come home to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.78,1:04:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆大叔微微笑\NUncle Sam is mild
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.91,1:04:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,平静有如孩子般\NHe's peaceful as a child
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.66,1:04:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,但是切忌让他闹\NBut never get him riled or you'll be whipped
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.53,1:04:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好莱坞 闭嘴\NHollywood, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.08,1:04:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 安静下\NCome on, pipe down.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.58,1:04:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴 衰人 - 闭嘴\N- Shut up, man. - Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.36,1:04:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我向上帝发誓 好莱坞 我要给你一枪\NI swear to God, Hollywood, I will shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.30,1:04:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别唱了 可以吗 当我们到那儿时再唱\NPut a sock in it, will you? Save the crowing for when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.91,1:04:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,娱乐一下而已\NKilljoy was here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.24,1:04:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,让路\NGive him room.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.38,1:04:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 小心 靠边\NClear! Clear! Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.56,1:05:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,美国陆军第96步兵师\NThe 96th...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.31,1:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都剩下些啥？\Nor what's left of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.25,1:05:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这些是他们的后备军\NThese are the guys we're replacing.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.18,1:06:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我觉得不错 - 安全\N- Seems good to me. - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.65,1:06:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这儿挺好 - 安全\N- As gold. - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.99,1:06:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,安全 中士\NAll clear, Sarge!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.67,1:06:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉格洛弗\NCaptain Glover.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.54,1:06:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉曼维 96师\NLieutenant Manville, 96th.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.87,1:06:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被派给您 长官\NWe've been assigned to you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.75,1:06:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.51,1:06:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- 大家给这些伙计弄点吃的 - 是 长官\N- Let's get these men some chow. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.59,1:06:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是中士豪厄尔\NThis is, uh, Sergeant Howell.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.20,1:06:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴见到你 长官 - 坐下\N- Good to meet you, sir. - Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.32,1:06:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,谁是多斯\NWho's Doss?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.93,1:06:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿\NOver there.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.84,1:07:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你是多斯\NYou Doss?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.35,1:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,伊夫·谢克特\NIrv Schecter.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.11,1:07:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我和佩吉在此\NYou, and me and Page here
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.93,1:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是本区仅有的医护人员 所以\Nare about the only medics we got left in this area. So,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.32,1:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们将一起工作\NI guess we're gonna be working together.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.13,1:07:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚从前线来\NYou just come off the line?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.06,1:07:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,情形如何\NWhat's it like?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.58,1:07:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我问了情形如何\NI said, What's it like?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.71,1:07:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,钢锯岭吗\NHacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.50,1:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们攻下六次\NWe climbed up six times.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.45,1:07:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我 六次被他们赶出\NSix times, they threw us off.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.84,1:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一次 基本上是全军覆没了\NLast time, there wasn't anything left of the 96th.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.69,1:07:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是畜生\NThey're animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.87,1:07:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,恶臭的畜生\NStinking animals.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.19,1:07:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,小日本不关心他们是死是活\NNips don't care if they live or die.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.66,1:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想死 他们不断袭击你\NThey want to die. They keep coming at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.96,1:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从不放弃\NAnd they ain't never going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.21,1:08:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,永不\NNever.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.83,1:08:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 伙计\NHere. Hey, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.47,1:08:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,日本鬼专门袭击伤员\NThe Japs deliberately target the wounded.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.70,1:08:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,去掉你所有的红十字标志\NLose all your Red Cross markings.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.62,1:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小日本极好枪击军医\NNips put a premium on shooting medics.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.85,1:08:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那白色的靶心\NThe white is a bull's-eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.80,1:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,拿去 我给你个新头盔\NHere, I got you a new helmet.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.92,1:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是均码的\NOne size fits all.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.61,1:08:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的目标\NThat's our objective.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.12,1:08:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,钢锯岭\NHacksaw Ridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.84,1:08:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们占领它\NWe take it,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.06,1:08:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,可能就拿下冲绳\Nmaybe we get Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.49,1:08:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拿下冲绳 我们就能占领日本\NWe get Okinawa, we take Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.58,1:08:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,吸口气\NTake a breather.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.62,1:08:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的海军朋友会温柔的请他们欢迎各位\NOur pals in the Navy are going to soften them up for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.19,1:09:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那死样没人能活\NNobody can survive that shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.61,1:09:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 但他们能\NOh, but they can.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.13,1:09:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,中尉\NLieutenant,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.34,1:09:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,此处的这些掩体 这里和这里 准确吗？\Nthese bunkers here, here and here, is that accurate?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.66,1:09:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\NYeah, there's three...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.66,1:09:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官 也许他们会从后面看 但这就是全部\NYes, sir, maybe a little further back, but it's all...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.49,1:10:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不同 那上边\NIt's all different up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.78,1:10:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,安全 上尉\NAll clear, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.86,1:10:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,战士们\NGents,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.73,1:10:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,出发\Nmove out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.11,1:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是血\NIt's blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.43,1:10:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,糟透了\NNo shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.58,1:10:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已不在堪萨斯了 多萝西\NWe're not in Kansas anymore, Dorothy.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.12,1:10:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,继续爬\NKeep climbing.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.62,1:10:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里\NHere, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.60,1:11:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来把你的手给我 让路\NComing through, make way. Out of the way.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.67,1:11:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,- 布朗 - 什么\N- Brown. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.86,1:11:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个给杰索普\NGive this to Jessop.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.03,1:11:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,下士\NCorporal!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.55,1:13:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\NIncoming!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.89,1:13:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.29,1:13:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\NGet down!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.20,1:13:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,他们到底在哪儿 我看不到他们\NWhere the hell are they? I can't see nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.24,1:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 隐蔽点 - 该死的在哪儿\N- Beats me, pal. - Where the...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.56,1:13:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,军医\NMedic!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.53,1:13:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,在这边\NWe're over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.43,1:13:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放在这儿 按住肠子 杰克\NPut your hand right here. Put your hand on there, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.74,1:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快 走 走\NCome on, move, move.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.68,1:13:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我们帮你找掩护\NCome on, we're going to get you under cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.48,1:14:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快 跟着我\NCome on, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.73,1:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着我 杰克\NCome with me, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.64,1:14:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,继续前进\NKeep moving forward! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.74,1:14:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看不到任何东西\NI can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.28,1:14:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 是那个吗 - 我不知打哪儿\N- Is that one? - I don't know. Just shoot!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.64,1:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们上\NAll right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.92,1:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,迪诺\NVito!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.72,1:14:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 糟糕\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.28,1:15:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 多斯 迪诺中弹 - 我来了\N- Medic! Vito's down! - I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.70,1:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我在这\NOkay. I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.09,1:15:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,让路\NGet out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.87,1:15:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你受伤了\NYou hurt?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.66,1:15:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我很好\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.84,1:16:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我帮你 拉尔夫 呼吸\NCome on, I got you, Ralph. Just breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.83,1:16:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸\NJust breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.13,1:16:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸\NJust breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.25,1:16:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系\NIt's okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.68,1:16:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸 拉尔夫 呼吸\NJust breathe, Ralph, just breathe.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.78,1:16:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮你 我帮你 我帮你\NI got you, I got you. I got you. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.63,1:16:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 嘿 给他一针吗啡再继续前进\NHey! Hey! Give him a shot of morphine and move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.35,1:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他挺不了一天\NHe's not going to last a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.63,1:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,求你 求你了多斯 别 别\NPlease. Please, Doss, no. No.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.96,1:16:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,别丢下我\NDon't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.10,1:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,别丢下我 请别丢下我\NDon't leave me. God, please don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.64,1:16:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我有孩子\NI've got kids!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.64,1:16:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,求你 别这样 请别丢下我\NPlease. Please, don't. Please, don't leave me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.91,1:16:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会离开\NI ain't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.83,1:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我会带你回家\NI'm going to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.08,1:16:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我会救你 拉尔夫 好吗\NI got you, Ralph. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.90,1:16:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我会带你回家\NI'm going to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.78,1:16:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,吗啡来了 吗啡来了\NHere comes the morphine. Here comes the morphine.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:59.10,1:17:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就会起作用 拉尔夫\NIt's going to kick in real quick, Ralph.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.67,1:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会转移你\NWe're going to get you shifted.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.83,1:17:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,担架\NStretcher!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.50,1:17:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,担架\NStretcher!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.58,1:17:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 起来 继续前进 孩子 - 我受伤了\N- Get up. Keep moving, son. - I can't, I'm wounded.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.75,1:17:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事\NThere's nothing wrong with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.00,1:17:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,倒霉 坚持 小子\NShit! Hang on, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.63,1:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,动起来 不当士兵就当死人\NMove. A sitting duck's a dead one.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.89,1:17:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,上 上 上\NMove. Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.01,1:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有个优先级\NThis guy's a priority.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.73,1:17:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,优先级？你还没有分类\NA priority? You ever heard of triage?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.80,1:17:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们送他们下去之前 他会死的\NHe'll be dead before we get him down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.05,1:17:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你又怎么知道\NYou don't know that!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.57,1:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,送他下去\NGet him down.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:42.01,1:17:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？\NAll right?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.24,1:17:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.20,1:17:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 好吧 走吧 - 很好\N- Okay. Okay. Go. - Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.03,1:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 老友 我们会送你回家\NIt's all right, buddy. We're going to get you home.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.30,1:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 救命 救命\NMedic! Help! Help.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.62,1:18:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得若我们看不见他们 他们也看不见我们\NI figure if we can't see them, then they can't see us neither.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.43,1:18:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\NHelp!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.27,1:18:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 弗兰克 你伤在哪儿？\NI got you, Frank. Where you hit?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.91,1:18:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我认为他们只是自作聪明 - 多斯 来吧 来吧\N- I think they can see us, smart ass! - Doss, come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.35,1:18:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,用手抓住我这儿\NGive me a hand here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.04,1:18:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下 长官\NGet down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.79,1:18:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,在那儿 掩体\NOver there! The bunkers.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.16,1:18:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了 最好呆下边 长官\NI see them. Better stay down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.80,1:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,发现敌人 正前方\NI got 'em, dead ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.69,1:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 对 我也看到了\NYeah, yeah I see 'em, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.39,1:18:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,准备好所有武器消灭他们\NPush in as close as you can. Give them everything you've got.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.86,1:18:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让武攻队从两侧围剿\NI'll send in the weapons team to flank them.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.59,1:19:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧点 你会完好如初 好吧？\NYou keep that tight, you're going to be right as rain. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.03,1:19:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我来吧 多斯 我来吧\NI got him, Doss. I got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.02,1:19:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你 快\NHere you go, come on now.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.03,1:19:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.87,1:19:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你干得可好？\NYou doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.35,1:19:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.64,1:19:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\NAnd, fire!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.45,1:19:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\NDown!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.15,1:19:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,狗娘养的\NSon of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.82,1:19:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你 接着打 - 遵命 长官\N- You, get on it. - Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.59,1:19:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,马上\NNow
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.83,1:19:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护他\NTake 'em. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.71,1:19:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,开火\NFire!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.15,1:19:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,烟雾弹\NSmoke!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.62,1:20:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护\NCover!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.22,1:20:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上 上 "食尸鬼"\NGo, go. Go, Ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.69,1:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,到那个坑里 待着不要动\NGet in the hole. Stay there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.10,1:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,上 上 史密提 我们掩护你 闪过去\NGo! Go, Smitty, we'll cover you. Leapfrog.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.18,1:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护\NCover.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.16,1:20:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,炸药包\NSatchel!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.92,1:20:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- "食尸鬼"- 知道了\N- Ghoul! - Clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.61,1:20:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 坚持住\NCome on, stick it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.77,1:20:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住 食尸鬼\NStick it, Ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.26,1:20:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护 掩护\NCover! Cover!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.30,1:21:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,狗日的\NSon of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.74,1:21:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护他\NCover his ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.48,1:21:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 军医 救救我\NMedic! Medic! Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.04,1:21:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,上\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.12,1:22:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,军医\NMedic!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.00,1:22:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里 用手按住它\NI'm here. Put your hand on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.31,1:22:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,用手按住它\NPut your hand on it!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.24,1:23:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,上 上 上\NGo, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.08,1:23:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,上 上 上\NGo, go, go! now
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.33,1:23:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"食尸鬼"\NGhoul.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.58,1:23:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"食尸鬼"\NGhoul.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.81,1:23:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧 你伤在哪儿？\NYou're okay. Where you hit?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.88,1:23:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你没伤着头没事的\NYou got a bump on the head, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.87,1:23:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫啥名\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.02,1:23:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 安迪 - 安迪啥\N- Andy. - Andy what?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.20,1:23:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪·沃克\NAndy Walker.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.57,1:23:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,外号\NAlso known as?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.58,1:23:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,- "食尸鬼" - "食尸鬼"\N- Ghoul. - Ghoul.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.82,1:23:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,"食尸鬼"你没事 你没事\NGhoul, you're okay, you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.89,1:24:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很称职 小伙子们 干得不错\NGood job, men. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.55,1:24:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就此过夜 我们守住本地\NDig in for the night. We hold this spot,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.62,1:24:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明天消灭剩下的山脊\Nwe mop up the rest of the ridge tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.96,1:24:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 小伙们\NOkay, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.56,1:24:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,给自己找个舒适安全角落或靠近掩体\NFind yourself a nice safe hole in or near the bunker.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.65,1:24:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我们每两小时换次岗\NRotate watch every two hours.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.65,1:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知那边是些啥\NWe don't know what's out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.10,1:24:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,死忠 愚蠢 烂人\NHeads down, asses lower.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.83,1:24:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不说英语的全毙了\NAnd shoot anything that don't speak English.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.50,1:24:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- 包括"老油条"？中士 - 尤其是他\N- Does that include Grease, Sarge? - Particularly him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.46,1:24:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不关心他是否需要尿尿或大号\NI don't care if you need to take a piss or a dump,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.80,1:24:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,单独去那边可不安全\Nit ain't safe to go out there alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.60,1:24:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底要去哪儿？多斯\NWhere the hell are you going, Doss?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.58,1:24:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那边还有很多伤员 中士\NStill more wounded out there, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.00,1:24:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他一起去\NI'll go with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.45,1:24:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,机灵点 注意四周\NBe smart. Keep your ears down.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.43,1:24:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 大家找个地儿\NAll right, let's find a spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.46,1:24:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利在首轮15分钟就挂了\NRinnelli and Henry dead in the first 15 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.48,1:24:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,直接挂掉\Njust straight off.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.20,1:24:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是直接挂掉\NStraight off.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.63,1:25:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得森 大力水手\NPeterson, Popeye.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.62,1:25:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,斯坦福和墨菲\NStandford and Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.76,1:25:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,佩吉 安戈\NPage and Unger.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.48,1:25:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,拉斯顿\NRalston.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.60,1:25:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,和平年代子葬父\N"In peace, sons bury their fathers,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.35,1:25:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,战争时期父葬子\Nin war, fathers bury their sons."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.44,1:25:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,别说丧气话好吗\NYou wanna stop spouting that crap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.57,1:25:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这帮不了任何人\NIt don't help none.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.29,1:25:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.99,1:25:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\Nyou got that right.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.97,1:25:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但不在此地\NNot here.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.28,1:25:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.30,1:25:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,给我那个\Ngive me that.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.18,1:25:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\NHey,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.10,1:25:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我们找到个腹部伤员\NHey, we've got an abdominal wound.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.99,1:25:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,小伙子需要血浆\NThis man is going to need some plasma.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.32,1:25:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 明白了 - 他和我们一起\N- You got it. - Leave him with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.65,1:25:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 没事的 他们会救你的\NOkay. You're okay now. They got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.07,1:26:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们找个窝呆呆\NShould we find a hole and dig in?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.62,1:26:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得行\NSounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.12,1:26:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,戴上头盔\NPut your helmet on.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.38,1:26:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你要吃那些\NYou ain't going to eat them?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.55,1:26:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不吃肉 你随意\NI don't eat meat. Help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.51,1:26:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了 你不吃\NOf course you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.04,1:26:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她是个不错的女子\NThat's one heck of a dame.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.18,1:26:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道你有她让我们很受打击 是吗？\NYou know you're fighting out of your weight class with her, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.97,1:26:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我知道\NYes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.35,1:26:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉她这些\NDon't tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.21,1:26:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她不会太喜欢我这样的男人\NShe'd be much happier with a man like me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.20,1:26:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 直到她了解你\NYeah, until she got to know you.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.75,1:27:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个混蛋 有时\NI'm an asshole sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.26,1:27:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有时\NSometimes?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.97,1:27:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 对 对\NYeah, all right. All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.00,1:27:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这些日本人很卑鄙\NThese Japs are sneaky.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.25,1:27:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我来站第一个岗\NI'll take first watch, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.66,1:27:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你眯会儿\NYou get some shut-eye.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.72,1:28:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,地狱之梦\NHell of a dream.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.02,1:28:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我梦见自己被杀\NDreamed I got myself skewered.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.85,1:28:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我毫无办法\NI couldn't do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.73,1:28:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,只需步枪\NRifle's just there.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.09,1:29:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,它不会咬人\NIt won't bite.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.71,1:29:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,对 那么\NYeah, it will.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.30,1:29:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你周围\NLook around you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.55,1:29:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,经历了我们这些遭遇\NAfter what we've just been through,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.04,1:29:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,任何理智的人都会尖叫着找寻武器\Nany sane man would be screaming for a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.05,1:29:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我从未声称自己理智\NI never claimed to be sane.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.03,1:29:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸是酒鬼\NMy daddy's a drunk.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.21,1:29:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,他屡戒屡犯多年 酒瘾缠身\NHe fought it for years, but it kind of got a hold of him hard.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.03,1:29:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,酒后失态\NMade him mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.76,1:29:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,至少你知道 何时我曾与\NLeast you knew him. Mine could have been any one
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.41,1:29:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,十人中的任何一位同在 而他们没有一个人该死\Nof 10 guys, and none of them worth a damn, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.89,1:29:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你妈妈养大了你\NSo, your momma raised you?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.40,1:29:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得她\NI knew her,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.29,1:29:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得她 但她把我丢给孤儿院 在我五岁时\Nbut she gave me to an orphanage when I was five.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.70,1:29:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,再没见过她\NNever saw her again.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.20,1:29:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我知如何快速行动\NI learned how to hate quick.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.49,1:29:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我识人更快 我则确实看错了你\NI learned how to judge people quicker, and I got you very wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.30,1:30:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我爸只是经常打我跟我哥 因为日升\NMy daddy used to beat me and my brother just because the sun rose,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.18,1:30:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,又因为日落 无缘无故打我们\Nand then whip us just because it set.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.95,1:30:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我能忍受那样\NI could take that...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.75,1:30:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但当他打妈妈时\N...but when he would do it to our momma...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.99,1:30:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开 婆娘\NGet away from me, woman!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.58,1:30:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,够了 不再 听清楚没\NThat's enough. No more. Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.94,1:30:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,扣下那该死的扳机\NPull the damn trigger.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.89,1:30:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 德斯蒙德 住手\NStop it! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.51,1:30:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但你并没杀他\NBut you didn't kill him?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.43,1:30:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在心里 我杀了\NIn my heart, I did.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.92,1:31:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为何我向上帝发誓\NSo that's why I made my promise to God,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.72,1:31:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我再也不去摸枪\NI ain't never going to touch a gun again.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.77,1:31:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧我不会给你我的 因为你是疯子\NWell, I ain't giving you mine, 'cause you're crazy.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:38.74,1:31:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,狗娘的\NSon of a...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.08,1:31:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,狗娘养的\NSon of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.20,1:32:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,行动 行动 让你们的屁股离开那儿\NMove, move! Get your asses over here.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.35,1:32:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,一起撤\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.30,1:32:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,回去 撤退 撤\NFall back, fall back! Go!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.15,1:33:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从地下冒出来\NThey're coming from underground.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.07,1:33:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,长官 这是贝克6队 请求立即支援\NSearchlight, this is Baker Six. Request immediate support.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.74,1:33:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 目标是北三零五一五 - 你没注意你在哪儿吗？\N- Target is Yoke-Tare-Five-One-Five. - Don't you notice where you are?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.88,1:33:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我有留意究竟在哪儿\NYes! Yes, I know that's where the hell we are,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.01,1:33:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可不想再呆在这儿\Nbut I don't expect to be here much longer!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:15.13,1:33:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫了火炮打击\NI called an artillery strike.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.80,1:33:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退 行动 行动\NFall back. Move. Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.97,1:33:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,撤退 快\NFall back! Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.42,1:33:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 兄弟 我在这 我在这\NHey, buddy. I'm right here. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.93,1:34:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.55,1:34:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,掩护我\NCover me.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.99,1:34:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,撤 撤\NGo, go!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.36,1:34:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,离开这儿 小子\NGet out of here, kid!
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.16,1:34:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 孩子\NCome here, son.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.92,1:34:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你知怎做 保持压住它\NYou know what to do. Keep pressure on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.30,1:34:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不需要血浆 把它给他\NNo! Don't need plasma. Give it to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.06,1:34:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,在那边\NOver there.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.52,1:34:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我会没事的 去吧 去吧\NI'll be okay. Go. Go.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.10,1:34:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,- 里斯 背他走 - 什么\N- Grease! Get Irv's back. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.96,1:34:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- 收到 好的 - 回头见\N- You got it, okay. - See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.94,1:34:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 来吧\NCome on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.43,1:35:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上行动 来吧 来吧\NWe gotta move right now. Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.31,1:35:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,来\NChange!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:46.20,1:35:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,人太多了 他妈的快退\NThere's too many, get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.99,1:35:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,撤 撤\NMove! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.69,1:36:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我很害怕 我很害怕 - 这能止痛\N- I'm scared. I'm scared. - It's going to help the pain.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.71,1:36:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不要 不要 你别这样 来吧\NNo, don't. Don't you do that. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.04,1:36:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 史密提留下陪我 我们得一起走\NCome on, Smitty, you stay with me. Let's go. We gotta move.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.28,1:37:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 嘿 - 是\N- Hey! - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.05,1:37:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- 帮我把他送下去 帮我把他送下去 - 好\N- Help me get him down. Help me get him down. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.61,1:37:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧让我们行动 来吧\NCome on, let's move. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.12,1:37:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,帮不了你 伙计 他走了\NCan't help him, buddy, he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.16,1:37:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有 - 来吧 我们要离开这儿\N- No. - Come on! We gotta get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:17.58,1:37:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.50,1:37:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快 走\NCome on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.13,1:37:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快 大家\NCome on. Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:32.89,1:37:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,离开山脊\NOff the ridge!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.45,1:38:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,他要我去哪儿\NWhat is it you want of me?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.60,1:38:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:30.53,1:38:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我听不到你\NI can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.57,1:38:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,军医 救我 救我\NMedic, help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.91,1:38:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\NHelp me!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.66,1:38:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.18,1:39:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会没事的 放松 放松\NYou're in good hands. Easy does it. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.64,1:39:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,六 八\N...six... eight...
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.48,1:39:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,十四\NFourteen.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.03,1:39:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,保障这些人的安全\NGet these men secured immediately.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.62,1:39:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 长官\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:14.80,1:39:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵 福特 有多少人？\NPrivate Ford, how many?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.34,1:39:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只有32个下来了 长官\NThirty-two only came down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.66,1:39:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝啊\NGood Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.87,1:39:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们四下找找 - 是 长官\N- Let's load 'em up. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.21,1:40:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哈利 我是德斯蒙德\NHarry. It's Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.50,1:40:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会医好你 你只需保持呼吸 好吗\NWe going to fix you up. You just got to keep breathing. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.38,1:40:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,上校想见你 长官\NColonel wants to see you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.06,1:40:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你的吉普\NI need your jeep.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.17,1:40:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你两个留此警戒 提防日本鬼子\NYou two stay here, keep watch, keep your eyes peeled for Japs.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.82,1:40:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不行 但是 - 留此 警戒\N- No, but... - Stay here! Keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.43,1:40:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 遵命 长官 - 遵命 长官\N- Yes, sir. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.58,1:40:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,救命 救我\NHelp. Help me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:31.56,1:40:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当心\NWatch out.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.80,1:40:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我救你\NWatch out. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:39.26,1:40:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,把手放上面 保持按住它\NPut your hand on it. Keep pressure on it.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.70,1:40:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回来 好吗？\NI'm comin' back. Okay? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.66,1:40:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别离开\NDon't leave me
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.13,1:41:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,轻些 伙计们 轻些\NEasy, fellas, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.90,1:41:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就放这儿\NHere we go.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.60,1:41:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好了伙计们 一起来 一 二 三\NOkay, guys, let's go. On the count of three. One, two, three.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.65,1:41:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,放\NMove.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:12.77,1:41:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,就没 军医来这里\NHelp, medic over here!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.98,1:41:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 伙计 坚持住\NIt's okay, buddy, hold it together.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:21.03,1:41:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来到悬崖边了 埃里克\NWe're at the edge, Eric.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.28,1:41:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只需坐稳 好吗 - 好\N- You just sit tight, okay? - okay
Dialogue: 0,1:41:45.47,1:41:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事的 埃里克 没事的 伙计\NYou're okay, Eric. You're okay, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.77,1:41:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋 这会起作用\NSon of a gun, this is going to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.06,1:41:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,每条腿一个 埃里克\NOne for each leg, Eric.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.03,1:42:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上帮你穿好 再放你下去\NWe're going to get you dressed up in a jiffy and get you down.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.19,1:42:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我救你\NI got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.57,1:42:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在救你 埃里克\NI got you now, Eric.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.45,1:42:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你得相信我 埃里克\NYou have to trust me now, Eric.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.56,1:42:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你得相信我\NYou're gonna have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.06,1:42:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,日本佬\NJaps!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.20,1:42:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我们的人 等等\NHold on, one of ours. Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.53,1:42:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快去 快去\NLet's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.40,1:42:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我救你 我救你\NI got you. I got you. I got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.94,1:42:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 我救你 你没事了 你没事了\NCome on, I got you. You're okay. You're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.80,1:42:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,汉克\NHank,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.74,1:42:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,又一个\Nanother one.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.76,1:43:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,上校 呼叫取消炮击钢锯岭 不能投弹\NColonel, call off the artillery attack on Hacksaw. Couldn't call it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.03,1:43:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,还有超过100人在那儿\NThere's still over 100 men left up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:08.60,1:43:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他们取消炮击钢锯岭\NTell them to call off the artillery on Hacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.16,1:43:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,埃布尔 贝克 壹 完毕\NAble-Baker-One ,over.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.04,1:43:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下 杰克 我给你喝的\NSit down, Jack. I'll get you a drink.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.86,1:43:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,只是失去掩护\NWe just lost our cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.06,1:43:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要开始了 我们赶紧行动\NThey're stirrin', we got to move. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.58,1:43:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,刚好\NAbout time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.76,1:43:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他们不断下来\NThey just keep coming by the...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:43.26,1:43:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好的 抬起来 - 我抬这边\N- OK, OK. Pick it up. - I got this.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.53,1:44:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,多斯\NDoss.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.51,1:44:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,多斯\NDoss.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.76,1:44:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,救命\NHelp.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:27.82,1:44:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\NHelp
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.45,1:44:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,救我\NHelp me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.44,1:44:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须要相信我\NYou're gonna have to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.66,1:44:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,呼吸\NTake a breath.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:44.40,1:45:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 伙计\NLet's go, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.27,1:45:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.42,1:45:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,杰克\NJack,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:50.38,1:45:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道你在那儿的人是死是活\Nyou don't know if your men up there are dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:52.53,1:45:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,没有援军 我们不能回到上边去\NYou can't go back up there without reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:54.40,1:45:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你会让剩下的人也送命 - 那就给我援军\N- You'll end up killing the rest of them. - Then give me the reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.68,1:45:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有新人 我没有任何连队\NI don't have any fresh men, okay? I don't have any troops.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:00.52,1:46:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,三个营被消灭在今天\NThree battalions got wiped out today.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:02.69,1:46:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,新兵到这儿还要一天多\NIt'll take more than a day to get men in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:05.44,1:46:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要他们早点到\NI need them faster than that.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.93,1:48:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系\NIt's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.71,1:48:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了 没事了\NIt's all right. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.10,1:48:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\NEverything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.66,1:48:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,吗啡 好的\NMorphine. It's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:02.28,1:49:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,皮尼克 皮尼克 皮尼克 我是多斯\NPinnick, Pinnick. Pinnick. It's Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.24,1:49:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我是多斯 安静 安静\NIt's Doss. Be quiet. Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.82,1:49:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来救你\NI got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.87,1:49:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你伤哪儿 - 我看不见\N- Are you hit? - Yeah. I can't see.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.25,1:49:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,安静 安静点\NBe quiet. Just be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.93,1:49:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,现在别动\NHold still now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.29,1:49:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我救你\NI got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:19.73,1:49:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,抓稳\NHold tight.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:21.80,1:49:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,弄好了 试着看 试着看\NThere you go. Try now. Try now.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.11,1:49:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我瞎了\NI thought I was blind!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.39,1:49:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘 冷静 你能走吗\NShh... Keep it down. Can you walk?
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.02,1:49:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.74,1:49:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们得离开这儿 好吗 快\NWe got to get out of here, okay? Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:49.93,1:49:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好了\NGood. Okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.30,1:49:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接住你了\Nwe got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.23,1:49:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接住你了\NWe got you.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.47,1:50:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 泰德\NHey, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:09.31,1:50:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 德斯蒙德 我会让你好起来的\NIt's me, it's Desmond. I'm gonna fix you up.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:14.48,1:50:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你准备离开这儿 - 我肯定\N- You ready to get out of here? - Sure am.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:32.33,1:50:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,恳请上帝\NPlease, Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:34.52,1:50:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再救一个\Nhelp me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.06,1:50:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再救一个\NHelp me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.86,1:51:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请让我再救一个\NPlease, help me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:27.97,1:51:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再一个\NOne more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:29.26,1:51:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再救一个\NHelp me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:43.11,1:51:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,再一个\NOne more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:45.80,1:51:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再救一个\NHelp me get one more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.88,1:51:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再一个\NOne more.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.49,1:51:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\NComing through.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.71,1:51:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙到底哪来的\NWhere the hell are these guys coming from?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.52,1:52:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,钢锯岭\NFrom Hacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.71,1:52:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我以为他们已撤完了 - 并非所有\N- I thought they pulled out. - Not all of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:03.56,1:52:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,某疯子在那里把伤员从顶上放下来\NSome nut's up there dragging wounded from the top.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:06.70,1:52:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至放下了几个日本佬\NEven lowered a couple of Japs.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:09.51,1:52:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们没能挺得住\NThey didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:10.89,1:52:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,回头直接带给你\NBack with you directly.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:13.34,1:52:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,轻点 轻点\NEasy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.42,1:52:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,满了 出发\NAll set, move out.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.35,1:52:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,到这儿来 到处都是日本人\NGet in here. There's Nips everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:52.66,1:52:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,狗娘养的 列兵"玉米秆"\NSon of a bitch. Private Corn Stalk.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.35,1:52:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你还真让人惊喜啊\NYou are nothing if not full of surprises.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:58.62,1:52:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要些吗啡？\NYou want some morphine?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.57,1:53:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 想得很 或者你给我一枪 - 好吧\N- Hell, yes. That or a bullet. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.64,1:53:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来了\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:04.83,1:53:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\NThere you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:09.36,1:53:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NAll right,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.59,1:53:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,放松 让我看看\Nlet me see. Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:12.66,1:53:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这样如何？好吧 不坏\NHow's this doing? Okay, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.42,1:53:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看\NLet me see.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.37,1:53:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我会做得比这还要糟\NIt looks much worse than it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:20.96,1:53:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但女孩们还是不会吻你\NGirls will still want to kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:24.38,1:53:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,中士\NSarge,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.24,1:53:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在此呆一会儿吗？\Nyou okay here for a while?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.72,1:53:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我还好 尽管离开\NYeah, fine. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:29.97,1:53:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我会回来\NI'm coming back.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.50,1:53:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好了？我们走 你跟我 来吧\NYou ready? Let's go. You and me, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:08.71,1:54:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉 有事你得瞧瞧\NCaptain. There's something you gotta see.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.97,1:54:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,整个夜里我们的人被一个个的放下来\NOur guys have been coming down in droves all night.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.30,1:54:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,而"好莱坞"在此 我从没想过还能再见此人\NAnd Hollywood's here. I never thought I'd see that guy again.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:18.77,1:54:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧跟我来 他在这儿\NCome on, follow me. He's right here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:24.30,1:54:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事\NWhat the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.68,1:54:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 长官\NHow you doing, sir?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.10,1:54:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 "帽子"\NHey, Cap.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.52,1:54:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,上尉\NCaptain.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:32.99,1:54:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- 很高兴看到你 孩子 - 格洛弗上尉 长官\N- It's good to see you, kid. - Captain Glover, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.14,1:54:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么下来的 孩子\NHow'd you get down, son?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.62,1:54:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是多斯\NDoss.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:38.92,1:54:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,豪厄尔仍在那儿\NHowell's still up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:40.58,1:54:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 豪厄尔和多斯做的\NWhat, Howell and Doss did this?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:43.12,1:54:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 长官 只是多斯\NMostly just Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.25,1:54:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,- 只是多斯？- 只是多斯\N- Just Doss? - Just Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.13,1:54:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对 多斯 那"懦夫"\NYeah, Doss, the coward.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.66,1:56:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你喜欢鞋上的枪 不是吗 - 给我这个\N- You're like gum on a shoe, ain't you? - Give me this.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:08.92,1:56:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,现在打靶太迟了 你不觉得\NIt's a bit late for target practice now, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:15.63,1:56:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 跳上来 - 你开玩笑吧\N- Jump on it. - You're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.68,1:56:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我来拖你\NNo, I'm going to drag you.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.43,1:56:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NLet's do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.43,1:56:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好没？- 好了\N- Ready? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.85,1:56:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:35.57,1:56:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有追兵\NWe got company.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.11,1:56:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:59.95,1:57:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得跳\NArms up.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.93,1:57:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你在耍我吧？"玉米秆"\NYou gotta be kidding me, Corn Stalk.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:03.20,1:57:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你是结单套 不是结胸罩\N"You're tying a bowline, boy, not building a bra."
Dialogue: 0,1:57:06.85,1:57:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.32,1:57:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好没？- 好了\N- Ready? - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:12.52,1:57:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,下去\NGet on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.38,1:57:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放下我 - 是 中士\N- Put me down! - Yes, Sarge.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:42.76,1:57:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- 中士豪厄尔 - 多斯还在那儿\N- Sergeant Howell. - Doss is still up there.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.01,1:57:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- 到底咋回事？- 他被日本佬尾追\N- What the hell? - He's got Japs on his tail.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:21.39,1:58:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我们接住他了\NWe got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:22.63,1:58:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 很好\NThat's good. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:24.88,1:58:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好 我们接住他了\NIt's okay, we got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:33.10,1:58:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 多斯\NIt's okay, Doss.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.12,1:58:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好了 多斯 - 你安全了\N- Come on, Doss, - You're safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:37.65,1:58:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好吧 - 多斯 你没事了\N- All right. - Come on, Doss. You ok
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.75,1:58:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德 你没事了 没事\NDesmond, it's all right, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:59.01,1:58:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德\NDesmond.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:02.93,1:59:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,放松 放松\NEasy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.74,1:59:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿 来吧\NHere, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:06.44,1:59:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下\NTake a seat.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:11.27,1:59:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你受伤了\NAre you wounded?
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.19,1:59:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:18.43,1:59:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.69,1:59:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大家立即送这名士兵去医疗篷\NLet's get this soldier to a hospital tent, right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:24.36,1:59:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来吧 现在放轻 - 放松 放松\N- Come on, easy now. - Easy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:26.91,1:59:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,腾个地方\NMake some space.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:16.08,2:00:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,伊夫在哪儿\NWhere's Irv?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:17.34,2:00:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 伊夫 你是说谢克特军医 - 是的\N- Irv? You mean, Schecter the medic? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:20.52,2:00:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他没能挺住\NHe didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:21.86,2:00:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他死于震伤\NHe died of shock.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.83,2:00:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,没有血浆\NNo plasma.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:25.42,2:00:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.08,2:01:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我只看到一个瘦小子 我不知你是谁\NAll I saw was a skinny kid. I didn't know who you were.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:10.18,2:01:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你比任何别的男人报效祖国\NYou've done more than any other man could have done
Dialogue: 0,2:01:12.32,2:01:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,所做的多得多\Nin the service of his country.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.64,2:01:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我此生从未如此看错人\NAnd I have never been more wrong about someone in my life.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:18.87,2:01:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望有天你能原谅我\NI hope one day you can forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:33.60,2:01:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们明天必须回到上边\NWe have to go back up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:38.33,2:01:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到明天是你的安息日\NI realize that tomorrow is your Sabbath.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:47.25,2:01:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人大多数不相信你所信仰的方式\NMost of these men don't believe the same way you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.79,2:01:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们如此相信\NBut they believe so much
Dialogue: 0,2:01:54.27,2:01:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多坚信\Nin how much you believe.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.97,2:02:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你在山脊上的所为就是奇迹\NAnd what you did on that ridge, it's nothing short of a miracle,
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.10,2:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想要一块\Nand they want a piece of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:06.75,2:02:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你 他们不会去那儿\NAnd they're not going to go up there without you.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:20.00,2:02:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底拖延什么 上尉\NWhat the hell is your delay, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:21.67,2:02:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该在10分钟前开始进攻\NYou were supposed to begin that assault 10 minutes ago!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:23.96,2:02:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们在等着 长官 - 等啥？\N- We're waiting, sir. - Waiting for what?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:29.18,2:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵多斯完成为我们的祈祷 长官\NFor Private Doss to finish praying for us, sir.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:32.01,2:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵多斯在为你祈祷？\NPrivate Doss is praying for you?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.84,2:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,列兵多斯到底是谁\NWho the hell is Private Doss?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:57.59,2:02:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去干活\NLet's go to work.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.53,2:04:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下 趴在地上\NGet down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,2:04:53.53,2:04:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,立即趴在地上 现在\NGet on the ground. On the ground. Now!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.40,2:05:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下 躺下 我有吗啡\NLay down, lay down. I got the morphine.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:40.99,2:05:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走 我们走 我们带这个人离开这儿\NLet's go, let's get these men out of here.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.80,2:05:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,走 走\NGo, go.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:48.58,2:05:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的圣经\NMy Bible...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.84,2:05:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我的圣经\NMy Bible.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:51.44,2:05:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的圣经\NMy Bible...
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.57,2:05:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,停下 停下 停下\NStop. Stop, stop, stop. Stop!
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.59,2:05:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我的圣经 我的圣经\NMy Bible, my Bible, my Bible.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:59.28,2:06:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:15.86,2:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你回家了\NYou're going home, Desmond.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.96,2:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已拿下钢锯岭\NWe've taken Hacksaw.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.78,2:07:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,等下 等下 德斯蒙德\NHold up, hold up! Desmond!
Dialogue: 0,2:07:28.24,2:07:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,德斯蒙德\NDesmond.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.91,2:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在祈祷\NI was praying the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.56,2:09:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是开始祈祷上帝请让我再救一个\NI just kept praying, "Lord, please help me get one more."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.84,2:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,当我救多一个 我说"好吧 上帝请让我再救一个"\NWhen I got this, I said, "Lord, please help me get one more."
Dialogue: 0,2:09:36.06,2:09:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为任何人都是错的\NI would say anyone is wrong
Dialogue: 0,2:09:37.92,2:09:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,若要去妥协他人的信念\Nto try to compromise somebody's conviction.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:40.13,2:09:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎是军队\NI don't care whether it's army
Dialogue: 0,2:09:42.09,2:09:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是什么\Nor what it is.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:43.68,2:09:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,当你持有信念\NWhen you own a conviction,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.19,2:09:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是笑话\Nthat is not a joke.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.49,2:09:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是你\NThat's what you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:52.74,2:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,即使我对他说那些关于携带步枪的事\NEven though I said those things to him in regard to carrying a rifle,
Dialogue: 0,2:09:56.68,2:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然而他永远不会站在我这边\Nthen he would never be by my damn side at all
Dialogue: 0,2:10:01.42,2:10:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他拿了枪\Nunless he had a rifle.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.08,2:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是从长远来看\NBut then, in the long run,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.82,2:10:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,发现他是一个活着的最勇敢的人\Nfinding out that he was one of the bravest persons alive.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.81,2:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,而让他停止挽救我的生命\NAnd then to have him end up saving my life
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.34,2:10:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,则会是对整件事的讽刺\Nwas the irony of the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:16.76,2:10:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,血顺着这家伙的脸跟眼流下\NBlood had run down into the fella's face and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:22.24,2:10:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当他开始呼喊军医的时候\NHe was laying there just groaning and calling for a medic.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:27.48,2:10:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我从水壶取水 拿出绷带\NI took water from my canteen, got some bandage,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.64,2:10:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我冲洗他的脸\Nand I washed his face.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.75,2:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,当我擦拭\NAnd when I wipe
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.97,2:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,当我擦拭 冲洗他的双眼 眼睛睁开了\Nwas washing his eyes, his eyes came open.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.49,2:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 他顿时亮了\NMan, he just lit up.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.13,2:10:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他说 我以为我瞎了\NHe says, "I thought I was blind."
Dialogue: 0,2:10:48.42,2:10:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如我没有任何东西\NAnd if I hadn't got anything more out of the war
Dialogue: 0,2:10:51.05,2:10:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,多于他给我的微笑 我不会得到很好的回报\Nthan that smile he gave me, I'd have been well repaid.
